mage.myqcloud.com%2FimageDir%2Ff32789ad2054d025564fae9fd9c1f3bbu5.jpg%22%2C%22tags%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22time%22%3A%222019-10-26%2011%3A04%3A33%22%7D\" data-alt=\"飞行员试戴新做好的头盔\"/>飞行员试戴新做好的头盔</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,1,4,0),(207,'台风过后日本潜艇出海训练 方向舵却转不动了','2019-10-26 22:21:36','<p class=\"otitle\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">（原标题：台风过后日本潜艇出海训练 方向舵却转不动了）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">【环球网报道 记者 徐璐明】台风过后，日本海上自卫队的舰艇纷纷恢复训练和部署，不过一艘亲潮级常规潜艇在出海时遇到了一些小麻烦。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">这艘亲潮级潜艇近日从横须贺军港驶出，然而其方向舵却被疑似台风期间吹来的漂流物卡住，无法转动。潜艇多次尝试调整方向舵后未能奏效，只好请来驻扎在横须贺港的水下处置队协助。潜水员搭乘小艇抵达潜艇尾部，进行水下摸排后成功解除了缠绕物，这艘潜艇才得以“脱身”。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: initial; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: initial; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: initial; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: initial; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/1620b238c310419ea640d0633da59a69.jpeg\" data-upload-link=\"%7B%22cover%22%3A%22%22%2C%22desc%22%3A%22QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20191026093542.jpg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22af6ef873e04108779e2d9bcfbbd6c61du5%22%2C%22size%22%3A102.77%2C%22width%22%3A900%2C%22height%22%3A522%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm1-1253159997.image.myqcloud.com%2FimageDir%2Faf6ef873e04108779e2d9bcfbbd6c61du5.jpg%22%2C%22tags%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22time%22%3A%222019-10-26%2009%3A47%3A58%22%7D\" data-alt=\"刚驶离码头的亲潮级潜艇就发现有些不对劲\"/>刚驶离码头的亲潮级潜艇就发现有些不对劲</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">在清除缠绕物期间，驻扎在厚木基地的美国海军第12直升机海上作战中队还出动一架MH-60S直升机前来协助，提供空中支援。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: initial; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: initial; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: initial; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: initial; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/477f1d4c0b15417ca133396514672e13.jpeg\" data-upload-link=\"%7B%22cover%22%3A%22%22%2C%22desc%22%3A%22QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20191026093618.jpg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22db467ceb6986e663e51275ec99c021dau5%22%2C%22size%22%3A67.03%2C%22width%22%3A900%2C%22height%22%3A504%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm1-1253159997.image.myqcloud.com%2FimageDir%2Fdb467ceb6986e663e51275ec99c021dau5.jpg%22%2C%22tags%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22time%22%3A%222019-10-26%2009%3A48%3A25%22%7D\" data-alt=\"潜艇方向舵被不明物体卡住，无法转动。\"/>潜艇方向舵被不明物体卡住，无法转动。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">亲潮级潜艇是日本自行研制的一款大型柴电动力攻击潜艇，较前一型春潮级潜艇有更良好的操控性能、潜航深度的增大、续航力增加、情报处理能力更优越。在亲潮级潜艇的基础上，日本又推出了更为先进的苍龙级，通过加长艇身换装了四台斯特林MK.3封闭循环发动机，使其成为东亚第一种配备不依赖空气推进系统 （即AIP）的柴电潜艇，大幅延长了持续潜航时间。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: initial; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: initial; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: initial; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: initial; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/4062172f1c8f4385b5b47f1487c7702e.jpeg\" data-upload-link=\"%7B%22cover%22%3A%22%22%2C%22desc%22%3A%22QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20191026093630.jpg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22d554ff026fe04b4adcb12f7b9f1dab9cu5%22%2C%22size%22%3A63.96%2C%22width%22%3A900%2C%22height%22%3A497%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm1-1253159997.image.myqcloud.com%2FimageDir%2Fd554ff026fe04b4adcb12f7b9f1dab9cu5.jpg%22%2C%22tags%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22time%22%3A%222019-10-26%2009%3A48%3A52%22%7D\" data-alt=\"潜艇方向舵被不明物体卡住，无法转动。\"/>潜艇方向舵被不明物体卡住，无法转动。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: initial; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretc