dth: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: initial; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: initial; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: initial; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/75acf5a63b8340179dd056e299420aa7.jpeg\" data-upload-link=\"%7B%22cover%22%3A%22%22%2C%22desc%22%3A%22QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20191026093738.jpg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22c665e6c2e63c3ce330dfb787ff97c4fcu5%22%2C%22size%22%3A98.19%2C%22width%22%3A900%2C%22height%22%3A572%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm1-1253159997.image.myqcloud.com%2FimageDir%2Fc665e6c2e63c3ce330dfb787ff97c4fcu5.jpg%22%2C%22tags%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22time%22%3A%222019-10-26%2009%3A48%3A52%22%7D\" data-alt=\"潜水员在水下对方向舵进行清理\"/>潜水员在水下对方向舵进行清理</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: initial; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: initial; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: initial; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: initial; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/2be29b7defde4739abd662cc8eb44e74.jpeg\" data-upload-link=\"%7B%22cover%22%3A%22%22%2C%22desc%22%3A%22QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20191026093754.jpg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%227b7efdb984e26c335e2d90fb0f780a5eu5%22%2C%22size%22%3A59.56%2C%22width%22%3A900%2C%22height%22%3A498%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm1-1253159997.image.myqcloud.com%2FimageDir%2F7b7efdb984e26c335e2d90fb0f780a5eu5.jpg%22%2C%22tags%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22time%22%3A%222019-10-26%2009%3A48%3A52%22%7D\" data-alt=\"成功处理缠绕物后，潜艇出港。\"/>成功处理缠绕物后，潜艇出港。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,2,4,0),(208,'俄媒：乌兹别克斯坦首次测试中国红旗9防空导弹','2019-10-26 22:22:15','<p class=\"otitle\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">（原标题：俄媒：乌兹别克斯坦首次测试中国红旗9防空导弹）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">【环球网军事报道】据俄罗斯卫星网10月25日报道，乌兹别克斯坦日前在库尔库杜克(Kulkuduk)试验场首次测试中国红旗-9远程地对空导弹（外销型号为“FD-2000”）。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">消息称：“测试FD-2000防空导弹旨在确保我国领空安全。”</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: initial; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: initial; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: initial; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: initial; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/c8f9949f19074087987a2b9d86fdd422.png\" data-upload-link=\"%7B%22cover%22%3A%22%22%2C%22desc%22%3A%221.png%22%2C%22id%22%3A%222c2e836e8c7ac1f8122b35b79bae484cu1%22%2C%22size%22%3A1.24%2C%22width%22%3A1304%2C%22height%22%3A734%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm1-1253159997.image.myqcloud.com%2FimageDir%2F2c2e836e8c7ac1f8122b35b79bae484cu1.png%22%2C%22tags%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22time%22%3A%222019-10-26%2009%3A59%3A03%22%7D\" data-alt=\"乌兹别克斯坦电视台曾公开展示从中国购买的FD-2000防空系统\"/>乌兹别克斯坦电视台曾公开展示从中国购买的FD-2000防空系统</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">报道称，红旗-9（HQ-9/FD-2000）是中国远程防空导弹系统，也是中国第三代防空导弹防御系统，可摧毁敌方任意作战高度的战机、巡航导弹和直升机。红旗-9还是中国首个具备拦截地对地战术弹道导弹的系统。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: initial; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: initial; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: initial; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: initial; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/0f96c4e78b0748dba124d4316ae656fd.jpeg\" data-upload-link=\"%7B%22cover%22%3A%22%22%2C%22desc%22%3A%222.jpg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%228b14a054840f9849fffbedb9ff807d0cu5%22%2C%22size%22%3A295.48%2C%22width%22%3A1010%2C%22height%22%3A758%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm1-1253159997.image.myqcloud.com%2FimageDir%2F8b14a054840f9849fffbedb9ff807d0cu5.jpg%22%2C%22tags%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22time%22%3A%222019-10-26%2009%3A59%3A30%22%7D\" data-alt=\"珠海航展上展出的FD-2000防空系统\"/>珠海航展上展出的FD-2000防空系统</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,1,4,0),(209,'中国海军训练舰首次访问惠灵顿,为期4天','2019-10-26 22:23:32','<p class=\"otitle\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">（原标题：中国海军训练舰首次访问惠灵顿，为期4天）&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img width=\"600\" height=\"397\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: initial; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: initial; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: initial; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: initial; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; height: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/fe5ff9ad4957427d945e95b757b5018b.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">执行远航实习和出访任务的中国海军训练舰戚继光舰10月26日上午抵达新西兰首都惠灵顿，开始对新西兰进行为期4天的友好访问。这是戚继光舰入列后首次访新，也是中国海军训练舰首次访问惠灵顿。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">上午10时，在舞狮表演的鼓乐声中，戚继光舰缓缓停靠惠灵顿港。中国驻新西兰大使馆工作人员、华侨华人和留学生代表，新西兰海军助理司令兼参谋长海耶斯上校、海军官兵代表、海军学员后备生学校学员代表等200余人到码头迎接。</span></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img width=\"600\" height=\"394\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: initial; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: initial; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: initial; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: initial; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; height: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/75a12b9ca2874670b9e087abf2c4f57a.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">从巴布亚新几内亚莫尔兹比港登舰跟训的2名新西兰籍和2名日本籍军官顺利结束训练并离舰。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">在新西兰期间，戚继光舰出访海上指导组组长喻文兵少将一行将拜会新西兰国防军副司令戴维斯少将、海军司令普罗克特少将。出访官兵将赴惠灵顿维多利亚大学参观交流。戚继光舰将举行甲板招待会，并向新西兰军方、当地市民和华侨华人、中资机构人员等开放参观。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">惠灵顿港位于新西兰北岛南端，濒临库克海峡东南侧，居南、北两岛联系的要冲，是新西兰第二大港。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img width=\"600\" height=\"397\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: initial; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: initial; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: initial; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: initial; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; height: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/11ac54f68f6a492b86fc85fc5a5674a0.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">戚继光舰以中国明代民族英雄戚继光命名，于2017年2月正式入列，是中国自主设计建造的吨位最大、现代化水平最高的专业训练舰。戚继光舰9月20日从中国辽宁大连某军港解缆起航，到访新西兰前，已成功访问文莱、东帝汶、巴布亚新几内亚等多个亚太国家，随后还将访问斐济。这是戚继光舰入列后第二次执行远航实习访问任务。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">（原题为《中国海军训练舰首次访问惠灵顿》）</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,1,4,0),(210,'库尔德武装开始撤离叙北边境 俄敦促美军走人','2019-10-26 22:24:14','<p class=\"otitle\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">（原标题：库尔德武装开始撤离叙北边境 俄敦促美军走人）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">俄罗斯外交部副部长谢尔盖·韦尔希宁24日确认，叙利亚库尔德武装开始撤离靠近叙利亚和土耳其边界的地区，落实俄罗斯和土耳其就叙利亚局势达成的共识。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">【监督库武撤离】</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">韦尔希宁说：“我们满意地看到，在索契达成的协议正在得到执行。每件事都正在落实。”</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">根据俄土总统在俄罗斯南部城市索契达成的谅解备忘录，库尔德武装人员和武器必须在150个小时内撤至距离边界30公里以外的区域。俄军宪兵和叙利亚“边防”人员23日中午开始进入土方军事行动以外的叙土边境地区，协助库尔德武装撤离。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">设在英国首都伦敦的“叙利亚人权观察组织”说，库尔德武装撤离东北部哈塞克省的一些据点。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">俄罗斯驻叙利亚部队发言人伊戈尔·谢里茨斯基告诉媒体记者，俄罗斯宪兵部队驻守在距离叙北边境城市艾因阿拉伯数公里的地方，“驻点距离叙土边界2公里。我们可以从那里清晰地看到边界以及那座城市周边的区域”。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">谢里茨斯基说，俄军驻点配备信号塔。俄方宪兵和叙利亚“边防”人员在那里共同监督库尔德武装撤离。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">【不催土军回撤】</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">俄罗斯副外长韦尔希宁24日在首都莫斯科告诉媒体记者，俄土达成的谅解备忘录没有规定土耳其军队在限定时间内撤走。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">他说，备忘录同样不适用于库尔德族平民。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">土耳其认定叙利亚库尔德武装“人民保护部队”是恐怖组织，与境内库尔德工人党同源、威胁土耳其国家安全。土军9日发起越境行动，试图把库尔德武装逐出土方准备在叙土边境设立的“安全区”。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">根据俄土谅解备忘录，库尔德武装撤离后，俄土29日开始将在叙利亚东北部纵深10公里范围内联合巡逻。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">记者提问联合巡逻指俄土士兵并肩行动，还是分头巡逻、相互协调，多名土耳其安全人士回答，土耳其方面正在考虑方案。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">【敦促美军走人】</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">俄罗斯总统新闻秘书德米特里·佩斯科夫24日敦促留驻叙利亚的美国军队离开。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">他说，“对驻叙美军，大家都知道我方立场”，“只有受叙利亚政府邀请的俄军部队才算合法驻留叙利亚”。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">应叙利亚政府邀请，俄罗斯2015年9月派军队进驻叙利亚，协助叙利亚政府军打击极端主义武装，帮助收复大片失地。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">俄罗斯新闻社24日以一名俄罗斯国防部人士为消息源报道，俄方打算向叙利亚增派276名宪兵和33套军事装备。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">美国赶在土军发动越境行动以前宣布从叙利亚北部撤军。五角大楼后续确认，驻叙美军暂时撤到伊拉克。但美国官员和媒体21日披露，美方考虑在叙利亚留下少量美军。（杜鹃）（新华社专特稿）</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,2,4,0);
INSERT INTO `t_news` VALUES (211,'美俄接连核军演，上万人参加，究竟意在何方？','2019-10-26 22:25:08','<p class=\"otitle\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">（原标题：美俄接连核军演意在何方？“后中导条约时期”值得关注的不止核武）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">近日，俄罗斯实施了代号为“雷霆-2019”的战略核力量演习，共有5艘核潜艇，105架飞机、213个导弹发射器和1.2万人参加。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/506faf1495444cd1afe2d52ef99f6bdd.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\"/><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><strong>俄军在演练中发射RS-24“亚尔斯”洲际弹道导弹。</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">在为期3天的演习中，俄军向位于阿尔汉格尔斯克州以及堪察加半岛的靶场发射了十数枚可以携带核弹头的巡航导弹和弹道导弹。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">而美国战略司令部于俄军演习结束次日开始举行“指挥与控制年度演习”，包括“警惕之盾-2019”和“环球雷霆”演习两部份，这一系列演习旨在检查美国国内各区域的战备，尤其是核战备情况。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">据外媒称，在国内进行核演习的同时，驻欧洲美军还与若干个欧洲北约盟国举行代号为“坚定正午”的军事演习，期间德军战机进行了B-61型核航弹挂载演练。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/f0dd4ed722894b22ae58e386b054f1e3.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\"/><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><strong>德军“狂风”战斗轰炸机，可以挂载B-61执行核轰炸任务。</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">俄罗斯往年也会进行类似的核战备演习，但往往只会简单公开报道甚至不报道，但今年的例行演习却不遗余力地大加宣扬。可见除了检验战略战备力量的纯军事目的外，还有着明确的政治目的。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">在今年8月“中导条约”终止后，美俄开始大力推进战略导弹武器研发。近期中东局势持续紧张，多方角力愈演愈烈，俄政府此番行动也是借演习的机会对外展示战略威慑力量。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">而以美国为首的北约在欧洲的核演习则更引人关注。今年7月，据北约某机构成员发布的文件揭露，美国在欧洲部署了大约150枚B-61核弹，这些核弹分别存放在比利时、德国、意大利、荷兰和土耳其的六个空军基地里。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/a44a03eec4684a6fa18adc95d6ec88f6.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\"/><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><strong>美军在欧洲储存的B-61核弹分布示意图。</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">在此次“坚定正午”演习中，德国空军演练了将存放在地堡里的B-61核弹运出，而后挂载在“狂风”战斗轰炸机上的一系列科目，不过出于安全考虑，随后的飞行演练并没有挂载核弹。除了德国，意大利空军也参加了演习，参演战机从荷兰沃尔克兰空军基地起飞，那里也储藏着B-61核弹。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/d21768d030b34f3f8185e24e599dfab0.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\"/><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><strong>今年3月，美军以“进行飞行训练”为由向英国陆续派驻了6架可以挂载核武器的B-52战略轰炸机，并数次飞临俄罗斯附近的勘察加半岛东部地区，被视为是针对俄罗斯的威慑行动。</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">当下，五个存有美军核弹的欧洲国家中，土耳其是最大的不确定因素。该国于9号发动了对叙利亚库尔德人的军事行动，总统埃尔多安态度强硬根本不理会美国的开战警告长驱直入，土耳其炮兵甚至还“误击”了美军在叙利亚的军事哨所。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">而存放在该国因吉利克空军基地里的约50枚核弹现在就成了美国的心腹大患，土耳其虽然签署了《核不扩散条约》与《全面禁止核试验条约》，但埃尔多安表示“不能接受其它国家不允许土耳其拥有核武器。”更有美国官员声称这些核武器已经成为了埃尔多安的“人质”。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/c3d0c94bc7ea46cb8d0ea1321d9defd0.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\"/><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><strong>B-61是美军使用时间最长的核武器之一，最新的B61-12型核弹的战斗部可在300吨至50000吨当量之间调节，以便对不同目标进行可控精确打击。图为地堡内存储的B-61核弹。</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">美国政府有这样的担心也并不奇怪。在2016年7月爆发的土耳其政变中，轰炸了政府大楼的F-16战机就是从因吉利克空军基地起飞的。随着埃尔多安对美国失去信任，这些核弹自然不适合继续存放在这里。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">当然起决定性因素的还是美俄，实际上两国在战略武器领域的军备竞赛已经悄然拉开了帷幕。2017年俄军将9M729型远程巡航导弹投入现役，据美方公开的研究数据显示，该弹最远射程可达2500千米，已经违反了“中导条约”，俄罗斯方面则予以否认。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/6573841f7ddf4cf88d62ea2dfcf07435.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\"/><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><strong>俄军9M729远程巡航导弹的发射筒，用“伊斯坎德尔-M”系统发射。</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">自此两国的中导问题逐渐公开化，并于不久前彻底终止了“中导条约”。也就是说，美俄间现在仅存在《新消减战略武器条约》这一项涉及战略核军力的军控条约，而这一条约的前景也岌岌可危。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">《新消减战略武器条约》签订于2010年，次年起正式生效。根据美国官方消息，截止2018年年初，美俄两国根据该条约都已将核弹头数量降至1550枚以下，运载工具的数量不超过800件，战略轰炸机和已部署弹道导弹的数量则减少至700件以下。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/246ccf4fe5cc47bc8c6911d0196612ef.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\"/><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><strong>俄军图-95和美军B-52战略轰炸机同框，两者均具备核打击能力。</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">美国总统特朗普上台后首次与普京通电话时称不愿意延期《新消减战略武器条约》，随后俄方曾数次与美方接触希望延续这一重要双边军控协议，但美国政府都不置可否，被外界认为是想拖到2021年该条约失效后不再续签。如果这一协议也遭终止，两国造成的核安全压力恐怕会只增不减。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">而且该条约还存在诸多漏洞，在实际执行过程中恐怕并不如理论上那么有效。其中最关键的一点是条约只对核武器的数量做了限制，所以并不影响两国对核武器进行技术升级。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">除了继续改造现有核武器外，美俄还开始在新型高超音速武器领域不断发力，谋求用新技术打破原有的战略平衡。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/d931ad775b324cad9e2e7b2b319d9e50.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\"/><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><strong>在军事技术日新月异的大背景下，原来的军控协定很难对类似AGM-183A这样的新型高超音速武器进行有效限制。图为B-52H战略轰炸机挂载AGM-183A进行试验。</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">俄国防部在2018至2025年装备规划中已经将高超音速武器列为研制重点。最高飞行速度为10马赫的“匕首”巡航导弹现已服役，而号称可以以20马赫速度飞行的“先锋”超音速飞行装置也很快会达到实用化水平。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/f5554bc6c9074ddc99d41cecd1952319.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\"/><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><strong>米格-31战机挂载“匕首”超音速巡航导弹。</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">而美国国防部则提出要建设“全球快速打击能力”，并计划于2020年前将高超音速武器部署到欧洲司令部和亚太司令部防区。现在美军各军种正在推进合计八个高超音速武器项目，2019年在该领域的经费预算约为7.769亿美元，而到了2020年这一经费预算预计将增长至16.6亿美元，足见美军对新战略武器的重视。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/b0debba6c34f4ed8a616596f606732ac.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\"/><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><div class=\"gg200x300\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(229, 229, 229); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); float: left; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 0; margin: 0px 40px 0px 0px; overflow: hidden; padding: 19px; position: relative; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><div id=\"ssp_6374560\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;\"></div><a class=\"ad_hover_href\" target=\"_self\" style=\"background: url(&quot;&amp;quot;https://yt-adp.ws.126.net/channel4/ad_3017_ajgf_20190221.png&amp;quot;&quot;) 0% 0% / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box transparent; bottom: 0px; color: rgb(15, 107, 153); height: 17px; left: 0px; position: absolute; text-decoration-line: underline; width: 30px; z-index: 10;\" href=\"http://\"></a></div><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><strong>美国洛克希德马丁公司关于各军种高超音速武器研制项目的展示页，该公司参加了八个项目中的七个。</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">总的来说，军控条约失效，地区冲突不止，以及新型核武器、高超音速武器等战略武器的成熟与扩散，给国际安全机制增加了更多不确定因素。如何建立一个长久普遍的和平国际环境，对各国的政治智慧将是个不小的考验。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,1,4,0),(212,'俄军赴塞尔维亚参加演习 S400和','2019-10-26 22:26:17','<p class=\"otitle\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">原标题：俄军赴塞尔维亚参加演习 S-400和&quot;铠甲-S&quot;部署亮相（图））</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img width=\"500\" height=\"Infinity\" title=\"1571984801737530.png\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: initial; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: initial; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: initial; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: initial; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 545px; vertical-align: top; width: 500px;\" alt=\"1571984801737530.png\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/b31005701d904d44ad181b3f3689eb2b.png\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">S-400防空导弹系统（图源：俄国防部）</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">海外网10月25日电&nbsp;</span>俄罗斯《消息报》25日援引俄国防部消息称，俄军派遣的防空营已抵达塞尔维亚，准备参加在此举办的“斯拉夫盾牌-2019”第二阶段演习。俄军的S-400防空导弹系统和“铠甲-S”弹炮合一防空系统将部署亮相。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img width=\"500\" height=\"Infinity\" title=\"1571985000146902.gif\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: initial; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: initial; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: initial; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: initial; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 545px; vertical-align: top; width: 500px;\" alt=\"1571985000146902.gif\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/5f666f4669864771866b3196b4238946.gif\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">“铠甲-S”弹炮合一防空系统（俄国防部视频截图）</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">据俄国防部公告，S-400防空导弹系统和“铠甲-S”弹炮合一防空系统，是俄军首次在国外部署类似武器系统参加军事演习。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">俄媒称，塞尔维亚也将部署空军和防空导弹系统参加演习。俄军将与塞尔维亚军队演练协同防空作业，将对模拟空中目标进行侦测、跟踪、识别并予以消灭。塞尔维亚主要任务是在复杂的干扰环境中进行实战计算，以击退大规模空中攻击。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img width=\"500\" height=\"Infinity\" title=\"1571985032101003.gif\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: initial; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: initial; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: initial; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: initial; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 545px; vertical-align: top; width: 500px;\" alt=\"1571985032101003.gif\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/18c01f57fc0a497589da43a4b7c9630d.gif\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">（俄国防部视频截图）</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">据悉，“斯拉夫盾牌-2019”是俄罗斯和塞尔维亚首次联合举行的演习。第一阶段演习于今年9月在俄罗斯南部阿斯特拉罕州举行。第二阶段在塞尔维亚境内举行，将持续至10月29日。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,1,3,4,0),(213,'英海军陷兵力困境：四分之一军舰不能出海','2019-10-26 22:26:58','<p class=\"otitle\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">（原标题：英海军陷兵力困境：四分之一军舰不能出海）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; list-style: outside none none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">参考消息网10月25日报道&nbsp;</span>英媒称，英国海军四分之一的军舰目前不能出海执行任务。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">据英国《泰晤士报》网站10月24日报道，英国国防大臣本·华莱士表示，英国皇家海军76艘军舰中，有四分之一无法执行任务。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">报道称，华莱士23日在英国国防特别委员会发表讲话说：“如果我能让更多现有军舰投入运转，就能在更高的自由度上实现我们的一些雄心和任务。我已向第一海军大臣（英国海军现役最高将领）明确表示，我的优先工作之一是让我们拥有的东西运转起来。”</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; list-style: outside none none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">据《泰晤士报》报道，华莱士表示，在英国海军6艘现役的45型驱逐舰中，只有3艘可以执行任务。</span>这种驱逐舰每艘造价10亿英镑，因为在海湾地区出现故障，无法适应温暖海域，所以需要接受维护。英国海军另一型重要舰只23型护卫舰的可用数量也很有限。今年7月，英媒曾报道说英国海军13艘护卫舰当中有6艘正在接受定期保养，无法参与部署。目前仍有4艘处于维护当中。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; list-style-image: none; list-style-position: outside; list-style-type: none; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 720px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/1dd18621f38b4336aad713c5508586bc.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">英国海军的“勇毅”号驱逐舰因为没人操作不得不停泊数月（英国《泰晤士报》网站）</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">英媒指出，英国海军将领和政界人士都对驱逐舰和护卫舰数量下降表示担忧。英国在上世纪80年代拥有50多艘驱逐舰和护卫舰，到2005年仍然拥有30多艘。英国海军传统上采取“三分法”管理舰队：三分之一执行任务，三分之一准备起航，三分之一维修保养。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">但华莱士表示，他决心提高军舰利用率。“你去财政部索要更多经费，财政部只会转过身去，说‘钱都给你们了，你看它们（指军舰）根本不工作’。想要购买更多新型舰艇就更困难了。”</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">英媒认为，英国海军由来已久的人员招募问题已经引发人员配置危机，尤其是高素质人才危机，导致一些军舰只能待在港口里。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">报道称，据了解，“勇毅”号45型驱逐舰和“兰开斯特”号23型护卫舰去年不得不停泊数月，因为缺乏操纵舰艇的人员。2艘军舰被用作水兵投入任务前的训练船，从此进入常年维护期。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">报道指出，英国海军正处于落实现代化计划的初期阶段，计划内容很可能包括派出更多舰艇进行“前沿部署”。这意味着要让军舰常驻海外，让轮流执行任务和结束任务的官兵乘坐飞机往返，而不是把军舰开回英国。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">据《泰晤士报》报道，短期维护同样可以在现场进行，工程师可以乘飞机去军舰部署的海域执行维护工作，便于军舰延长海上停留时间。遇到长期改装计划可能还是需要舰艇返回英国船厂。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">报道指出，“蒙特罗斯”号23型护卫舰正在进行的试验被认为比较成功。“蒙特罗斯”号目前正与英国4艘扫雷舰及皇家海军后勤舰艇部队“卡迪根湾”号船坞登陆舰一道驻扎在巴林。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,1,4,0),(214,'土官员:土将保留打击在叙北部残留恐怖分子的权力','2019-10-26 22:27:33','<p class=\"otitle\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">（原标题：土官员：土将保留打击在叙北部残留恐怖分子的权力）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">中新网10月25日电 据俄罗斯卫星网报道，土耳其常驻联合国代表费里敦·瑟纳尔勒奥卢在联合国安理会会议上表示，该国将保留打击叙北部“和平之泉”行动残留恐怖分子的权力。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><img title=\"报道指出，炮击行动在一小时内即扩大至叙北部拉卡省的艾因伊萨市。\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: initial; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: initial; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: initial; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: initial; border-top-width: 0px; cursor: pointer; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 700px; vertical-align: middle;\" alt=\"点击进入下一页\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/8eb98aab28fd41628c7f0dc670ce49b2.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">资料图：土耳其在叙利亚北部发起军事行动，炮击行动很快扩大至叙北部拉卡省的艾因伊萨市。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">瑟纳尔勒奥卢称：“对于‘和平之泉’行动区可能残留的恐怖分子，土耳其将保留自卫的权力。”</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">他强调，土耳其将根据国际人道主义法，一直与恐怖分子作斗争。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">他补充道：“就像埃尔多安总统多次表示的一样，土耳其不可能，也不会容忍我国边境附近的任何恐怖主义行动。恐怖组织可以使用不同的名称和形式，可以采取各种策略，但我们对恐怖分子的警惕性将保持不变。”</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">9日，土耳其总统埃尔多安宣布在叙利亚北部发动代号为“和平之泉”的军事行动，打击库尔德工人党和恐怖组织“伊斯兰国”。17日，美国和土耳其达成协议，决定暂停行动120小时，允许库尔德武装从土叙边境30公里缓冲区撤离。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">22日，俄罗斯总统普京与土耳其总统埃尔多安会晤，就叙利亚局势商定相互谅解备忘录。根据这份备忘录，10月23日12:00起，俄军警与叙利亚边防部队会进入叙土边界叙利亚一侧‘和平之泉’行动区以外地区，协助库尔德人民保护部队撤到距叙土边界30公里以外，且后撤工作应在150个小时内完成。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">此后俄罗斯与土耳其将在“和平之泉”行动区以西和以东距叙土边界10公里地区进行联合巡逻，卡米什利市除外。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,1,5,4,0),(215,'美媒：土耳其可能放弃西方武器 转向中俄等国购买','2019-10-26 22:28:24','<p class=\"otitle\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">（原标题：美媒：土耳其可能放弃西方武器 转向中俄等国购买）&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">【环球网报道 记者 徐璐明】自土耳其在叙利亚开展“和平源泉”军事行动以来，北约多国陆续宣布对土耳其实施武器禁运，但土耳其方面表示禁运的影响并不大，因为该国有着一定的武器制造能力，还可以从俄罗斯、中国等国找到替代方案。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">美国《防务新闻》网站10月24日报道称，土耳其的一些北约盟国已经暂停对土耳其的武器销售，以谴责土耳其对叙利亚的军事入侵行为，但土耳其的专家和官员们对武器禁运并不在意，他们说，禁运对于土耳其开展军事行动能力的影响微乎其微。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: initial; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: initial; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: initial; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: initial; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/011938d144da4fd3a5a17225ad1003d0.jpeg\" data-upload-link=\"%7B%22cover%22%3A%22%22%2C%22desc%22%3A%226-1.jpg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%225d5dde075d29063ec0677eca6a66ff2au5%22%2C%22size%22%3A801.51%2C%22width%22%3A1920%2C%22height%22%3A1280%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm1-1253159997.image.myqcloud.com%2FimageDir%2F5d5dde075d29063ec0677eca6a66ff2au5.jpg%22%2C%22tags%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22time%22%3A%222019-10-25%2010%3A40%3A25%22%7D\" data-alt=\"中国的HQ-9防空系统曾在土耳其武器竞标中胜出\"/>中国的HQ-9防空系统曾在土耳其武器竞标中胜出</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">报道称，包括法国、瑞典、捷克、挪威、荷兰、西班牙、德国等国已经对土耳其实施武器禁运，以回应土耳其发动针对叙利亚的代号为“和平源泉”的军事行动。据美国国防部的一名高级官员透露，本月早些时候，特朗普政府宣布了针对土耳其在叙利亚军事行动的制裁措施，特朗普还在推特上威胁称，如果安卡拉采取任何他认为“禁止”的行动，他将彻底摧毁土耳其的紧急。但在10月23日特朗普又表示，他计划取消对土耳其最近军事行动的所有制裁。此前曾有报道称，美土双方达成了新的停火协议。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">对于武器禁运一事，土耳其一名高级外交官员说：“我们从这些国家进口的武器是有限的，没有人可以垄断任何武器系统，我们可以很容易地从其他供应商处获得（武器）”。他还表示，非西方的供应商也非常渴望取代西方制造商。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">土耳其负责武器采购的最高官员、国防部副部长伊斯梅尔说：“这些（武器禁运）都不会影响我们，我们已经对替代来源和本地生产采取了预防措施。”他表示，行动中使用的大多数武器系统，包括直升机、智能弹药、火箭弹、步枪、装甲车和电子战系统等，都是由土耳其当地企业提供。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: initial; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: initial; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: initial; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: initial; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/ffa339d25f604d2c99ee9f5fbb2534d6.jpeg\" data-upload-link=\"%7B%22cover%22%3A%22%22%2C%22desc%22%3A%226-2.jpg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%225ed299d89a3dfdf09955cd335cb16d4du5%22%2C%22size%22%3A492.17%2C%22width%22%3A1920%2C%22height%22%3A1080%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm1-1253159997.image.myqcloud.com%2FimageDir%2F5ed299d89a3dfdf09955cd335cb16d4du5.jpg%22%2C%22tags%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22time%22%3A%222019-10-25%2010%3A41%3A14%22%7D\" data-alt=\"俄罗斯极力向土耳其推销苏-57隐形战机\"/>俄罗斯极力向土耳其推销苏-57隐形战机</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">然而，土耳其军方也确实经历了暂时的弹药短缺，一位不愿透露姓名的土耳其安全官员告诉《防务新闻》说：“我们经常从西方购买的一些弹药库存出现短缺，但很快就被俄罗斯的供应所取代。”</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">报道称，一位驻扎在安卡拉的防务分析人士指出，乌克兰、白俄罗斯、巴基斯坦、韩国和中国都是土耳其替代弹药的来源国家。不难想象，俄罗斯会填补西方高科技系统在土耳其的空白，为了报复土耳其购买俄制S-400防空导弹系统，美国暂停了土耳其在F-35联合攻击战斗机项目中的伙伴关系。之后，土耳其转向莫斯科寻求临时解决方案，以增强其战斗机部队的实力。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,27,4,2),(216,'奚梦瑶生下长孙还不够?四太:至少生三个越多越好','2019-10-26 22:29:50','<p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img class=\"content-picture\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.6em; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0.6em; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" alt=\"奚梦瑶生下长孙还不够?四太:至少生三个越多越好\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/068a752a57c247b285d7797a1ce21ac3.jpeg\"/></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img class=\"content-picture\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.6em; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0.6em; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" alt=\"奚梦瑶生下长孙还不够?四太:至少生三个越多越好\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/d79ea0d9da5848cbbc351096f9e571f4.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">赌王四太梁安琪</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><strong>网易娱乐10月26日报道&nbsp;</strong>成功抱上孙子的赌王四太梁安琪，近日一改奚梦瑶怀孕时的低调，频频现身奚梦瑶所在的医院探视儿媳和孙子，脸上始终洋溢着满满的笑容，得孙欣喜之情溢于言表。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">10月25日傍晚四太再度现身医院探望小孙子，同时出面接受早已等候多时的记者们的采访。四太透露这次不光去看了孙子，同时还会去看望下赌王。不过四太否认有直接抱着孙子去见赌王，称这种事情儿子儿媳们会自己去处理。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">如今何猷君奚梦瑶已经成功产下家族长孙，未来是否让儿子儿媳继续追生？对于这问题，四太则是直接向儿子儿媳喊话：“至少生三个，越多越好，多少都没问题！”四太还直言会有很大的奖励送给奚梦瑶，她表示奚梦瑶怀孕很辛苦，她身为旁观者也能感受到奚梦瑶的不容易，如今奚梦瑶平安生下了男孙，她自然不会怠慢对方，承诺一定会大礼奉上。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">近年来，四太因为女儿何超盈突然宣布未婚怀孕、儿子何猷君迅速与奚梦瑶订婚被外界认为是在发动了“生子大战”。不过即使遭受质疑生子争产，四太如今似乎依旧不受舆论所动，始终坚持多生多养。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">下个月赌王即将迎来98岁大寿，自从传出病危住院后已经许久不见露面，但根据四太爆料赌王老人家状况还好，看到孙儿照片很开心。赌王98大寿当天为了孙儿罕见现身也未必没有可能。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img class=\"large\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top; width: 600px;\" alt=\"奚梦瑶生下长孙还不够?四太:至少生三个越多越好\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/714bde938034485f958d82c1ed7b6d36.jpeg\" data-loaded=\"0\" data-loadfunc=\"0\"/></p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,1,2,0),(217,'张雨绮直言羡慕素人简单的生活 坚守的防线做自己','2019-10-26 22:30:32','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 640px; vertical-align: middle;\" alt=\"张雨绮\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/108fab0b219c43e9a1abc0b362fe6fea.png\"/>张雨绮</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><strong>网易娱乐10月26日报道&nbsp;</strong>25日，《各位游客请注意》更新，张雨绮在节目中直言很羡慕素人，想过简单的生活，“和最喜欢的人简简单单牵手走在马路上，也被别人说成1234567”。她表示自己一直在很反抗圈子里的东西，但也在坚守自己的防线，“我也受到了很多伤害，并没有觉得自己做这些事情是不对的。还是做自己，还是义无反顾、勇往直前。” 此前，有八卦媒体拍到张雨绮和张钱豪深夜在路边等车。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,1,2,0),(218,'网友图书馆中偶遇章泽天 破“不读书”质疑','2019-10-26 22:31:24','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img style=\"border: 0px currentcolor; display: block; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/465d117689cc4d46ac7620435d5f37d9.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><strong>网易娱乐10月26日报道</strong> 近日，有网友在社交平台上晒出在大学图书馆中与章泽天的合照。照片中，章泽天素颜现身，坐在图书馆里学习，虽然没有精心打扮，但依然皮肤白皙，女神范十足。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">此前，章泽天经常晒出在英国参观游玩的照片，有网友对她的留学生活提出质疑，留言道“你读书吗 每天”，章泽天则罕见回怼网友，“我没发照片的日子都在读书”。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: initial; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: initial; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: initial; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: initial; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; height: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/15f6b58ee5b140be9f7f0504218e2749.jpeg\"/></p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,1,2,0),(219,'权志龙正式退伍 获上千人迎接人气不减当年','2019-10-26 22:32:42','<div class=\"post_text\" id=\"endText\" style=\"border-top: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); clear: both; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin: 0px; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px 0px 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; width: auto;\" jcid=\"5611\"><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"权志龙正式退伍 获上千人迎接人气不减当年\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/9831584bb6d6462cbbae162d1caa4bac.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; bo