, serif; font-size: 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: 宋体, serif; font-size: 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span><img width=\"0\" height=\"0\" src=\"https://img2.cache.netease.com/nocache/statistic/mod003.gif\" border=\"0\" style=\"border: 0px none currentcolor; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-size: 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: top; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: 宋体, serif; font-size: 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><div class=\"end-text\" id=\"endText\" style=\"clear: both; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin: 0px; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px 0px 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; width: auto;\" jcid=\"5611\"><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\"></p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\"><strong>网易娱乐10月26日报道&nbsp;</strong>今天，权志龙完成国防义务后从龙仁陆军地面作战司令部正式退伍，权志龙在现场发表感想称“顺利结束了兵役，谢谢大家的等待。”据韩媒统计，来自中日韩等国的超3000名粉丝和记者将到现场等候。</p></div><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,1,2,0),(220,'汪小菲吐槽小S不好好穿衣：姐妹性格差十万八千里','2019-10-26 22:34:01','<p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/5925ffff8ef84bd18963b70ec7e587db.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\"/><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">汪小菲吐槽小S“又不好好穿衣”</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 640px; vertical-align: middle;\" alt=\"大小S和汪小菲\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/44d06ae29809404192890adef5a82e9d.jpeg\" longdesc=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/ent/transform/545/w630h715/20191025/d07b-ihmipqw3140431.jpg\" data-link=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/ent/transform/545/w630h715/20191025/d07b-ihmipqw3140431.jpg\"/>大小S和汪小菲</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><strong>网易娱乐10月25日报道&nbsp;</strong>10月24日晚，汪小菲在微博分享了一则小S的一则新闻，新闻中小S穿浴袍装花式凹造型，露肩秀腿玩性感，他转发并评论称：“又不好好穿衣！你们家的妹和你们家的姐性格完全差了十万八千里！”</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">网友见状纷纷笑倒：“小S：诶，小菲你什么意思？”“突然想起汪小菲那句：我们家的女儿一定要穿的像样！”随后汪小菲删除了此条微博。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,1,2,0),(221,'《吻别》作曲殷文琦因胃癌去世 曾与多名歌手合作','2019-10-26 22:34:56','<p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 640px; vertical-align: middle;\" alt=\"知名音乐制作人殷文琦\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/52b218aaeb514c73bfc9c35a9ad30cd9.png\" longdesc=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/ent/transform/223/w436h587/20191025/c7c8-ihmipqw5336925.png\" data-link=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/ent/transform/223/w436h587/20191025/c7c8-ihmipqw5336925.png\"/>知名音乐制作人殷文琦</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><strong>网易娱乐10月25日报道&nbsp;</strong>知名音乐制作人殷文琦15日因胃癌过世，享年54岁，他曾写过多首脍炙人口的歌曲，其中又以1993年为张学友创作的《吻别》最为著名。晚年他与女儿、女婿一同住在北京，因罹患胃癌，饱受病魔之苦，3月回台医治，15日因第三次手术失败，不幸病逝，告别式将于11月23日于台北第二殡仪馆举行。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">殷文琦擅长作曲、编曲，曾以张镐哲的《北风》拿下第二届金曲奖最佳作曲人奖，并以张学友的《吻别》夺得第五届金曲奖最佳编曲人奖；其中《吻别》在台湾销售量就达136万张，帮助张学友收获人气，他更获张学友点名感谢。他也与刘德华、周华健、谭咏麟、叶蒨文、陈淑桦、张雨生等港台歌手合作，并曾任宝丽金、波丽佳音唱片公司音乐总监，为1987至1998年的华语乐坛，贡献不少作品。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,12,2,1);
INSERT INTO `t_news` VALUES (222,'中超-马尔康点球绝杀扎哈维平纪录 华夏2-1富力','2019-10-26 22:37:58','<div class=\"post_text\" id=\"endText\" style=\"border-top: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); clear: both; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin: 0px; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px 0px 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; width: auto;\" jcid=\"5611\"><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\">网易体育10月26日报道：</p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\">北京时间10月26日15:30，2019赛季中超联赛第27轮比赛继续进行，河北华夏主场迎战广州<a title=\"富力\" href=\"https://sports.163.com/keywords/5/c/5bcc529b/1.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">富力</a>。上半场，马斯切拉诺点球被<a title=\"程月磊\" href=\"https://sports.163.com/keywords/7/0/7a0b670878ca/1.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">程月磊</a>扑出，<a title=\"扎哈维\" href=\"https://sports.163.com/keywords/6/4/624e54c87ef4/1.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">扎哈维</a>挑射破僵并追平艾克森创下的2014中超单赛季进球纪录；下半场，<a title=\"王秋明\" href=\"https://sports.163.com/keywords/7/8/738b79cb660e/1.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">王秋明</a>助攻马尔康头球破门扳平比分，<a title=\"董学升\" href=\"https://sports.163.com/keywords/8/6/84635b665347/1.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">董学升</a>头球中框。补时阶段，马尔康打入点球，华夏幸福完成绝杀。</p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\"></p></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: 宋体, serif; font-size: 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: 宋体, serif; font-size: 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: 宋体, serif; font-size: 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: 宋体, serif; font-size: 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><div class=\"nph_gallery\" id=\"gallery166690\" style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-size: 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 10px 0px; position: relative; white-space: normal;\"><div class=\"nph_bg\" style=\"background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: transparent; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; opacity: 1; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; width: 100%;\"><div class=\"nph_photo\" id=\"modePhoto166690\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; width: 100%;\"><div class=\"nph_photo_view\" style=\"height: 400px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; position: r