-style: none; outline-width: medium; width: 100%;\"></a></div><div class=\"nph_photo_next\" style=\"background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: transparent; background-image: url(&amp;quot;http://img1.cache.netease.com/cnews/img/gallery11/bg06.png&amp;quot;); background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: auto; height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px; top: 0px; width: 50%;\" jcid=\"5421\"><a class=\"nph_btn_nphoto\" id=\"photoNext166690\" hidefocus=\"true\" href=\"https://sports.163.com/19/1026/17/ESEAQJLB00058780.html#p=ESE6VMHA0B6P0005NOS\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); cursor: url(&quot;http://img2.cache.netease.com/utf8/gallery/img/cursor_right.cur&quot;), auto; display: block; height: 100%; outline-style: none; outline-width: medium; width: 100%;\"></a></div><div class=\"nph_photo_viewlarge\" style=\"background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: transparent; background-image: url(&amp;quot;./img/magnifier.png&amp;quot;); background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; cursor: pointer; height: 26px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; opacity: 0.5; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; position: absolute; right: 20px; top: 32px; width: 26px;\" data-link=\"http://sports.163.com/photoview/0B6P0005/166690.html\"></div></div></div><div class=\"nph_photo_ctrl\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 221, 221); float: right; font-family: Arial; line-height: 1; margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px;\"><ul style=\"float: right; list-style-image: none; list-style-position: outside; list-style-type: none; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;\"><img width=\"0\" height=\"0\" src=\"https://img2.cache.netease.com/nocache/statistic/mod003.gif\" border=\"0\" style=\"font-family: sans-serif; border: 0px none currentcolor; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: top;\"/></ul></div></div></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: 宋体, serif; font-size: 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><div class=\"end-text\" id=\"endText\" style=\"clear: both; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin: 0px; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px 0px 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; width: auto;\" jcid=\"5611\"><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\"></p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\">【本场概况】</p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\">中超联赛26轮战罢，广州富力8胜5平12负积29分排名第12位，上轮联赛，广州富力主场1-3不敌山东鲁能，近5轮联赛1胜2平2负。河北华夏幸福7胜5平14负积26分排名第13位，上轮联赛，河北华夏幸福客场1-4不敌江苏苏宁，近5轮联赛2胜3负。两队中超历史交战8场，富力和华夏2胜3平2负，两队平分秋色。</p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\">【精彩瞬间】</p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\">开场第6分钟，华夏前场左路直塞肋部，王秋明禁区内左侧倒三角传中，皮球被程月磊封堵，李提香停球直接停给了马尔康，马尔康转身右脚射门被挡出。</p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\"><strong>开场第8分钟，姜至鹏前场左路传中，皮球打在禁区内弋腾张开的手臂上，主裁判在经过与VAR视频裁判连线后判给华夏一粒点球，马斯切拉诺操刀右脚推射，皮球被程月磊神勇扑出。</strong></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"中超-马尔康点球绝杀扎哈维平纪录 华夏2-1富力\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/cd105025a1b7421da0d9d04d378a3785.gif\"/><br/></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"中超-马尔康点球绝杀扎哈维平纪录 华夏2-1富力\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/8f86f392a40349f3bf9c25cc5f8e6864.gif\"/></p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\">第20分钟，富力快速反击，唐淼前场右路右脚弧线球传中，扎哈维门前头球攻门高出。第25分钟，姜至鹏左脚任意球直接射门，皮球越过人墙被程月磊飞身扑出。第30分钟，华夏快速反击，董学升中线附近送出绝妙直塞球，费尔南多带球突入禁区面对出击的程月磊射门被挡出，费尔南多起身横传中路，张呈栋和马尔康连续两点包抄射门被挡出。第36分钟，萨巴前场中路送出直塞球，扎哈维插入禁区右脚推射，皮球被池文一抱住。</p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\"><strong>第38分钟，唐淼后场送出过顶长传找扎哈维，华夏后卫潘喜明防守漏人，扎哈维插入禁区左脚挑射打破僵局，扎哈维联赛第28粒进球，追平艾克森2014赛季中超联赛单赛季进球纪录，华夏0-1富力。</strong></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"中超-马尔康点球绝杀扎哈维平纪录 华夏2-1富力\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/239857b52e10467b88adaf47ff7a4b5e.gif\"/></p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\">第43分钟，姜至鹏前场左路左脚传中，董学升禁区中路左脚扫射踢呲，皮球偏出右侧立柱。上半场，河北华夏幸福主场0-1落后广州富力。</p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\">易边再战第49分钟，马斯切拉诺任意球吊入禁区内，董学升禁区内左侧近在咫尺的垫射高出。第54分钟，姜至鹏开出前场右侧角球至禁区内，马尔康中路头球攻门高出。2分钟后，富力快速反击，萨巴前场右路横传转移，扎哈维插入禁区单刀左脚射门，皮球被池文一挡出。1分钟后，萨巴禁区内左侧左脚低射，皮球偏出右侧立柱。</p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\">两队互有攻守，比赛陷入僵持阶段，第61分钟，费尔南多前场右路送出直塞球，马尔康插入禁区右脚捅射，皮球被程月磊封堵。2分钟后，马斯切拉诺开出前场右侧角球，皮球被顶出，马斯切拉诺右路再度传中，任航头球攻门高出。第67分钟，费尔南多禁区内右侧横传，王秋明故意漏过皮球，无人盯防的马尔康禁区内右脚推射，皮球被池文一没收。</p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\"><strong>第69分钟，姜至鹏左路直塞，王秋明左脚传中，马尔康高高跃起力压戈腾头球破门扳平比分，华夏1-1富力。</strong></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"中超-马尔康点球绝杀扎哈维平纪录 华夏2-1富力\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/b5cc43228678460cbfdfc3aae306fffe.gif\"/></p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\">第78分钟，马斯切拉诺任意球吊入禁区内，董学升头球攻门，皮球击中横梁弹出。</p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\">第81分钟，姜至鹏前场左路左脚弧线球传中，马尔康俯身头球冲顶，皮球高出横梁。第87分钟，华夏开出前场左侧角球至禁区内，任航头球攻门，皮球被挡出。华夏连续角球传中，又是任航头球攻门，皮球被程月磊扑出。</p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\">伤停补时阶段，晋鹏翔推人送点，主裁判艾堃查看VAR后判罚点球，马尔康一蹴而就。但是由于华夏幸福球员提前进入禁区，艾堃判罚点球重踢，马尔康再次将点球打进。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"中超-马尔康点球绝杀扎哈维平纪录 华夏2-1富力\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/fdd9bd5324934c7fa9d050d553308cc7.gif\"/><br/></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"中超-马尔康点球绝杀扎哈维平纪录 华夏2-1富力\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/e0be718b7b574eb08d1108c0bd3c772d.gif\"/><br/></p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\">出场阵容：</p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\">河北华夏幸福（532）：33-池文一；11-姜至鹏、26-姜文骏、23-任航、37-潘喜明、28-张呈栋；32-费尔南多、14-马斯切拉诺、15-王秋明；9-董学升、10-马尔康；</p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\">替补球员名单：1-耿晓峰、5-罗素、18-冯刚、26-姜文骏、38-张威（U23）、45-龚秋乐（U23）、51-刘径（U23）；</p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\">广州富力（4231）：1-程月磊；2-邹正（87′，16-陈俊乐）、18-弋腾、27-晋鹏翔、20-唐淼；35-李提香（82′，4-张功）、23-卢琳；13-叶楚贵（74′，33-金波）、10-萨巴、32-陈志钊；7-扎哈维；</p><p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em;\">替补球员名单：22-韩佳奇（U23）、9-桂宏、19-姜积弘；</p></div><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,1,3,0),(223,'官宣！同曦男篮签约哈达迪 大帝成球队第四外援','2019-10-26 22:38:35','<p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">网易体育10月26日报道：</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><a href=\"http://cba.sports.163.com/team/Te012/\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">北京</a>时间10月26日晚上，<a href=\"http://cba.sports.163.com/team/Te005/\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">江苏</a>同曦<a title=\"男篮\" href=\"https://sports.163.com/keywords/7/3/75377bee/1.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">男篮</a>宣布签约CBA老熟人哈马德-哈达迪，哈达迪成为球队的第四名外援。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/208a61ec6fe94e55be5ed62169b1f063.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\"/><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">目前<a title=\"同曦队\" href=\"https://sports.163.com/keywords/5/0/540c66e6961f/1.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">同曦队</a>拥有、盖尔雄-亚布塞莱、约瑟夫-杨和贝南-雅克查理、和哈马德-哈达迪4名外援，由于他们拥有亚洲外援资格，新赛季可以注册3名外援，球队表示期待哈达迪的到来在提升内线高度的同时也能够丰富球队的战术体系，增强球队的阵容深度。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/3d5158e1b40e4d1285b595ae95ef3be7.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\"/><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">【纯中锋来啦！】各位媒体朋友，球迷朋友们：</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">我俱乐部已于近日与伊朗国手，CBA老熟人哈马德-哈达迪（Hamed Haddadi）达成协议，待向CBA联盟正式报送哈达迪的注册材料并经审核、公示通过后，他将成为球队第四外援，代表同曦队征战即将拉开大幕的2019-2020赛季CBA联赛。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">1985年出生的哈达迪今年34岁，2013年加盟CBA的他先后效力于四川、<a href=\"http://cba.sports.163.com/team/Te030/\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">青岛</a>、<a href=\"http://cba.sports.163.com/team/Te008/\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">新疆</a>。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">2015-16赛季，再度加盟四川队的哈达迪带领球队在总决赛中以4-1的大比分击败<a href=\"http://cba.sports.163.com/team/Te011/\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">辽宁</a>队豪夺总冠军，而他也以场均21.6分19.2篮板2.2助攻1.8抢断1.8盖帽的统治级表现收获了总决赛MVP。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">上赛季，哈达迪曾短暂地效力于新疆队，22场比赛，场均贡献10.5分10.7篮板3.1助攻1.6盖帽。其中在新疆103-97战胜上海的比赛中，哈达迪16投8中，砍下28分的同时还抢下了惊人的25个篮板（前场篮板9个，后场篮板16个），是球队获胜的关键人物。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><div class=\"gg200x300\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(229, 229, 229); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); float: left; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 0; margin: 0px 40px 0px 0px; overflow: hidden; padding: 19px; position: relative; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><div class=\"at_item right_ad_item\" style=\"line-height: 0; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; position: relative; width: 300px;\" requesturl=\"https://nex.163.com/q?app=7BE0FC82&amp;c=sports&amp;l=133&amp;site=netease&amp;affiliate=sports&amp;cat=article&amp;type=logo300x250&amp;location=12\" adtype=\"rightAd\"></div><a class=\"ad_hover_href\" target=\"_self\" style=\"background: url(&quot;&amp;quot;https://yt-adp.ws.126.net/channel4/ad_3017_ajgf_20190221.png&amp;quot;&quot;) 0% 0% / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box transparent; bottom: 0px; color: rgb(15, 107, 153); height: 17px; left: 0px; position: absolute; text-decoration-line: underline; width: 30px; z-index: 10;\" href=\"http://\"></a></div><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">34岁的年纪已不算年轻，但在上月刚结束的男篮世界杯中，哈达迪用自己的实际表现向外界证明了自己无愧于<a title=\"伊朗队\" href=\"https://sports.163.com/keywords/4/0/4f0a6717961f/1.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">伊朗队</a>的当家领袖。5场比赛，场均出场30分钟，贡献14.6分10.8篮板4.4助攻1.2盖帽，效率值达到19.4，这五项数据均在伊朗队内排名第一。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">首场对阵波多黎各的比赛中，哈达迪在终场前4秒命中高难度逆天3分，帮助球队将比分追至81平，尽管最终伊朗队惨遭对手绝杀，但哈达迪的这记3分成为当天比赛日的最佳镜头之一。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">新赛季还未开打，已有多支球队签下了候补外援，我们也期待哈达迪的到来在提升内线高度的同时也能够丰富球队的战术体系，增强球队的阵容深度。值得一提的是，哈达迪和雅克查理同为伊朗队队友，我们也相信两人多年来培养的默契度将对球队后续的技战术磨合带来积极的影响。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,1,3,0),(224,'嘘声与欢呼中厄文飙中制胜三分 KD为他起立庆祝','2019-10-26 22:39:08','<p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">网易体育10月26日报道：</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">在篮网同尼克斯的一场同城大战中，凭借厄文最后关键时刻的1球，篮网最终113-109取胜，厄文交出26分、5助攻、3抢断，运动战19投8中。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/e6aa12eaed5541d68e76c4c4f91e2934.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\"/><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">在篮网的揭幕战上，其实厄文就展示了相当不错的状态，他轰下50分，虽然最终未能够帮助篮网在加时取胜，但也创造了篮网的队史赛季首战得分纪录，有意思的是，那场比赛最后时刻厄文也是有关键球机会，他险些丢球却最终还是调整过来成功出手，赛后也收获了前队友勒布朗的称赞。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">今天这场比赛最后时刻依然激烈，最后半分钟双方分差仍只有1分，厄文站了出来，他在外线运球，面对防守人来了一记单腿的远投，球中！现场爆发巨大声浪，这其中有惊叹，但嘘声也不少，毕竟这场比赛虽然是篮网主场，但尼克斯作为同城球队在这里的球迷也不少。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><div class=\"gg200x300\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(229, 229, 229); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); float: left; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 0; margin: 0px 40px 0px 0px; overflow: hidden; padding: 19px; position: relative; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><div class=\"at_item right_ad_item\" style=\"line-height: 0; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; position: relative; width: 300px;\" requesturl=\"https://nex.163.com/q?app=7BE0FC82&amp;c=sports&amp;l=133&amp;site=netease&amp;affiliate=sports&amp;cat=article&amp;type=logo300x250&amp;location=12\" adtype=\"rightAd\"></div><a class=\"ad_hover_href\" target=\"_self\" style=\"background: url(&quot;&amp;quot;https://yt-adp.ws.126.net/channel4/ad_3017_ajgf_20190221.png&amp;quot;&quot;) 0% 0% / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box transparent; bottom: 0px; color: rgb(15, 107, 153); height: 17px; left: 0px; position: absolute; text-decoration-line: underline; width: 30px; z-index: 10;\" href=\"http://\"></a></div><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">回顾厄文这场比赛，他在首节进攻感觉并不太好，运动战只有2次出手，而且没有投中，次节他的状态慢慢提升，长距离投篮和篮下进攻都有建树。第3节厄文的效率又有起伏，此节他仅有1个运动战入球，来自于突破，另外4次出手都打了“铁”。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">但关键的末节，厄文提升了进攻端的侵略性，单节7次出手，内外结合，给予尼克斯相当大的威胁。事实上，篮网上半场建立了不错的领先优势，但下半场不断被追回去，末节更是输给尼克斯，如果不是厄文此节得分在线，恐怕比赛胜负难测。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">最后，当厄文飙中那个关键3分，场边观战的杜兰特也是兴奋地站起来，和队友一起庆祝。厄文也收获了他在篮网生涯的首场胜利。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,3,3,0),(225,'柯洁删除蛋爆了微博:我错了,我软了,我就是个弟弟','2019-10-26 22:42:15','<p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">网易体育10月26日报道：</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">奚梦瑶产子登热搜第一直接显示“爆”，而当天关乎人命的社会新闻显示“新”，<a title=\"柯洁\" href=\"https://sports.163.com/keywords/6/e/67ef6d01/1.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">柯洁</a>对此相当不满，发文炮轰，“卧佛了。热搜两个完全不知道是谁的人下个蛋显示个爆？？？是蛋爆了嘛？？？死了那么多人的事情只显示个新？？？”，目前，柯洁已经删除了该条<a title=\"微博\" href=\"https://sports.163.com/keywords/5/a/5fae535a/1.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">微博</a>，和粉丝在互动中表示，&quot;我已经把那条微博删除 ，<a title=\"知错\" href=\"https://sports.163.com/keywords/7/e/77e59519/1.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">知错</a>了，我在网络上就是个弟弟，女菩萨说的对 ，错了不狡辩，我已经软了。”</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img alt=\"柯洁删除蛋爆了微博:我错了,我软了,我就是个弟弟\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/866b47ea15f9423985ab5d8d5a50fce2.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\"/><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">相关阅读：<a style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); line-height: 1; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://sports.163.com/19/1026/19/ESEGJD7A00058782.html\" target=\"_self\" urlmacroreplace=\"false\">怒了! 柯洁:要赶尽杀绝吗? 双手双脚支持男女平等</a></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><a style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); line-height: 1; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://sports.163.com/19/1025/07/ESAKO90J00058782.html\" target=\"_self\" urlmacroreplace=\"false\">谁说女子不如男?生命最后时刻她比任何人都&quot;爷们&quot;</a></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"柯洁删除蛋爆了微博:我错了,我软了,我就是个弟弟\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/894350025c554900bc21a2eae29cb8ae.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\"/></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"柯洁删除蛋爆了微博:我错了,我软了,我就是个弟弟\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/142a0a47f65e4e27a94743ac8cd3165b.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\"/><br/></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"柯洁删除蛋爆了微博:我错了,我软了,我就是个弟弟\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/97f14119813a4127a6d5fe97d940dc3a.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\"/></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"柯洁删除蛋爆了微博:我错了,我软了,我就是个弟弟\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/0ea2061403984e88a6a6df8a641ee1c7.png?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">今天凌晨，柯洁发长文解释，“第一首先想说，我很尊重女性，而且我觉得每一位母亲都很伟大，请不要自己对号入。如果非要觉得我冒犯到你家女性了，我只能说我很抱歉。真没那个意思和本事。第二说我蹭热度的 真给整乐了，我又不是明星需要这种热度吗，我就是个嘴臭的网络暴民。第三说我不配世界冠军的再次把整乐了，世界冠军是用配的，笑了，我觉得您配 ?有一说一我嘴臭我承认 ，我真没想到微博人民真有这么多人相比较时事新闻，更喜欢喜欢<a title=\"娱乐圈\" href=\"https://sports.163.com/keywords/5/3/5a314e505708/1.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">娱乐圈</a>。我觉得我需要更进一步的优化，带来的不好影响给当事人大伙说句不好意思添麻烦了，知错了，再也不会提热搜这茬，<a title=\"古德\" href=\"https://sports.163.com/keywords/5/e/53e45fb7/1.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">古德</a>拜。”</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,1,3,0),(226,'塔图姆25+9+4绿军擒猛龙 布朗25+9西亚卡姆33+8','2019-10-26 22:42:59','<p style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">网易体育10月26日报道：</p><p style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">新赛季NBA常规赛全面开打，波士顿凯尔特人队（1胜1负）拿到赛季首胜。塔图姆得到25分、9个篮板、4次助攻和3次抢断，布朗也有25分和9个篮板，第四节关键时刻海沃德和布朗各中一记三分为球队确立胜局，凯尔特人队在主场以112-106险胜多伦多猛龙队（1胜1负）。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-align: center; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/0d68d032171246a483b5e35159d180fa.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; vertical-align: top;\"/><br/></p><p style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">凯尔特人队的塔图姆得到25分、9个篮板、4次助攻和3次抢断，布朗得到25分、9个篮板和4次助攻，沃克得到22分和6个篮板，海沃德得到15分和8个篮板，斯马特得到10分。猛龙队的西亚卡姆得到33分和8个篮板，洛里得到29分、4个篮板和7次助攻，伊巴卡得到13分和8个篮板，阿奴诺比得到9分和8个篮板。</p><p style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">凯尔特人队让泰斯出任首发中锋。开赛后两队争夺激烈，场上多次出现平分，15平后斯马特和塔图姆分别跳投命中，凯尔特人队拉开领跑。鲍威尔和戴维斯分别命中三分，塔图姆回应一个三分球，凯尔特人队以22-21领先1分结束首节。</p><p style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">塔图姆用扣篮开启第二节，约翰逊还击三分，他率队连得5分实现反超。双方之后各得几分，布朗打3分成功引领球队打出7-0的小高潮，本节进行了4分40秒时凯尔特人队以34-30领先。猛龙队外线再次开火，洛里命中2个三分球，范弗利特和西亚卡姆各中一记三分，他们带领球队打出14-4的反击高潮，半场前3分钟时猛龙队以44-38反超。斯马特、沃克、海沃德和威廉姆斯轮流进攻得手，凯尔特人队连拿8分再次领跑。西亚卡姆又中三分，塔图姆两罚全中，半场战罢凯尔特人队以50-49领先。</p><p style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">凯尔特人队的布朗上半场得到13分，塔图姆得到11分；猛龙队的洛里得到11分，西亚卡姆得到10分。</p><p style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">海沃德在第三节开始后率先命中三分，洛里手感不错，一人独得11分，猛龙队以60-59再次反超。布朗转身跳投命中，西亚卡姆进攻发力又拿9分，阿奴诺比也命中三分，他们率队打出12-5的进攻高潮，本节还有4分25秒时猛龙队以72-66领先。塔图姆和沃克先后投中三分，西亚卡姆三分回应，猛龙队仍有3分优势。塔图姆又得4分帮助球队反超，范弗利特和西亚卡姆轮流投中三分，猛龙队以7-0的小高潮结束第三节，他们以82-76领先。</p><p style=\"font-family: simsun; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">最后一节开始后两队争夺更激烈，双方展开对攻战，伊巴卡命中三分，猛龙队以98-93领先。沃克、布朗和海沃德联手6分帮助球队反超，西亚卡姆转身跳投还击，威廉姆斯上篮得手，塔图姆三分中的，第四节还有4分30秒时凯尔特人队以104-100领先。猛龙队连追4分扳平，海沃德和布朗各中一记三分，凯尔特人队在第四节还有2分45秒时以110-106领先。急于追分的猛龙队连续打铁，阿奴诺比和洛里也出现失误葬送追分机会，塔图姆两罚全中，凯尔特人队以112-106获胜。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,1,3,0),(227,'史上最奇葩点球!还没出界呢 热身球员就禁区停球了','2019-10-26 22:43:43','<p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">网易体育10月26日报道：</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">在足球场上，被吹<a title=\"点球\" href=\"https://sports.163.com/keywords/7/b/70b97403/1.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">点球</a>的方式堪称五花八门。在今天凌晨一场德乙联赛中，<a title=\"波鸿\" href=\"https://sports.163.com/keywords/6/e/6ce29e3f/1.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">波鸿</a>队得到的点球很可能是最奇葩的。在<a title=\"皮球\" href=\"https://sports.163.com/keywords/7/a/76ae7403/1.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">皮球</a>完全出界前，对方场边热身球员把球停回场内，波鸿因此得到了一个点球。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">在德乙第11轮中，波鸿客场对阵基尔荷尔施泰因。第9分钟时，韩国球员李在城为主队打破僵局，他近距离补射破门。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img alt=\"史上最奇葩!球还没出界呢 热身球员一脚踢回去了\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/f73e1e5307914c459aa829397bd1be2a.gif\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\"/><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">在第38分钟时，奇葩点球出现了。波鸿球员冈武拉右脚大力低射，皮球大大偏出球门。在皮球即将完全出底线的一刹那，热身中的主队球员埃贝魏因伸脚将球停回了场内。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img alt=\"史上最奇葩!球还没出界呢 热身球员一脚踢回去了\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/2975b701f6d84a5eb4a8aaeb6c99995d.gif\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\"/><br/></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img alt=\"史上最奇葩!球还没出界呢 热身球员一脚踢回去了\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/9b25dadcd7dd4bf983eb9aeda2778723.gif\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\"/><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">埃贝魏因这个下意识的举动，却犯下了大错。主裁在观看VAR后确认，皮球当时并没有完全出界。按照规则，未经主裁允许进入场地的球员如果干扰比赛，那就会被判罚直接任意球。由于埃贝魏因是在禁区内触球的，因此被判了个点球。埃贝魏因被黄牌警告，冈武拉点球破门扳平比分。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">在上半场补时阶段，基尔荷尔施泰因也获得了一个点球。<a title=\"塞拉\" href=\"https://sports.163.com/keywords/5/5/585e62c9/1.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(15, 107, 153); text-decoration-line: underline;\">塞拉</a>左脚推射球门左下角，波鸿门将里曼反应神速将球扑出。不过塞拉在第52分钟将功赎罪，在接到厄兹詹左路横传后，塞拉前点左脚抽射破门，基尔荷尔施泰因最终2-1赢得了胜利。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img alt=\"史上最奇葩!球还没出界呢 热身球员一脚踢回去了\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/75807ea6ee6c4da09763bd940444bde2.gif\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\"/></p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,7,3,1),(228,'国家制度和法律制度，习近平这样论述','2019-10-26 22:46:18','<p class=\"otitle\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">（原标题：国家制度和法律制度，习近平这样论述）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">【学习进行时】国家制度和法律制度与国家治理体系和治理能力现代化息息相关。9月24日，习近平总书记主持中共中央政治局第十七次集体学习，对中国特色国家制度和法律制度进行了深入阐释。新华社《学习进行时》摘引总书记讲话中的精辟论述，与您一起学习。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">一个历史性课题，贡献中国智慧和中国方案</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">建立什么样的国家制度，是近代以来中国人民面临的一个历史性课题。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">实践证明，我们党把马克思主义基本原理同中国具体实际结合起来，在古老的东方大国建立起保证亿万人民当家作主的新型国家制度，使中国特色社会主义制度成为具有显著优越性和强大生命力的制度，保障我国创造出经济快速发展、社会长期稳定的奇迹，也为发展中国家走向现代化提供了全新选择，为人类探索建设更好社会制度贡献了中国智慧和中国方案。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">四大优势，植根中华民族5000多年文明史</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">中国特色社会主义国家制度和法律制度，植根于中华民族5000多年文明史所积淀的深厚历史文化传统，吸收借鉴了人类制度文明有益成果，经过了长期实践检验。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">一是坚持党的领导的优势。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">二是保证人民当家作主的优势。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">三是坚持全面依法治国的优势。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">四是实行民主集中制的优势。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">做到两个“要”，把制度优势转化为治理效能</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">制度的生命力在于执行。要强化制度执行力，加强制度执行的监督，切实把我国制度优势转化为治理效能。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">◆各级党委和政府以及领导干部要增强制度意识，善于在制度的轨道上推进各项事业。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">◆广大党员、干部要做制度执行的表率，引领全社会增强制度意识，自觉维护制度权威。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">构筑三个体系，为坚定制度自信提供理论支撑</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">要加强对中国特色社会主义国家制度和法律制度的理论研究，总结70年来我国制度建设的成功经验，构筑中国制度建设理论的学术体系、理论体系、话语体系，为坚定制度自信提供理论支撑。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">要加强制度宣传教育，特别是要加强对青少年的制度教育，讲好中国制度故事，引导人们充分认识我们已经走出了建设中国特色社会主义制度的成功之路，只要我们沿着这条道路继续前进，就一定能够实现国家治理体系和治理能力现代化。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,1,1,0),(229,'中国营商环境全球排名跃升至第三十一位','2019-10-26 22:46:59','<p class=\"otitle\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">（原标题：中国营商环境全球排名跃升至第三十一位）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">本报北京10月24日电 （记者曲哲涵）北京时间10月24日上午10时，世界银行正式发布《2020营商环境报告》。报告显示，我国营商环境总体得分77.9分（即中国达到了全球最佳水平的77.9%），比上年上升4.26分；排名跃居全球第三十一位，比去年提升15位。我国已连续两年被世界银行评选为全球营商环境改善幅度最大的10个经济体之一。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">在世界银行10项评估指标中，中国有8项指标排名上升，比去年多1项。其中，办理建筑许可排名提升88位至第三十三位，保护中小投资者排名提升36位至第二十八位，办理破产排名提升10位至第五十一位，跨境贸易排名提升9位至第五十六位，纳税排名提升9位至第一百零五位，获得电力提升两位至第十二位，执行合同排名提升1位至第五位，开办企业排名提升1位至第二十七位。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">按照党中央、国务院决策部署，今年以来，国务院职能转变协调办、财政部会同司法部等十余个有关部门和京沪两市政府，对标国际先进、对接国际通行规则，于年初制定专项改革任务台账，明确改革目标、责任部门、时间节点。截至目前已完成了130余项改革举措，在保护中小投资者、办理建筑许可等体制机制改革方面实现了重大突破，进一步增强了我国营商环境的国际竞争力。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">财政部表示，下一步将继续会同有关部门和参与全球评估的地方政府，深入贯彻新发展理念，大力度深化改革、扩大开放，坚持市场化、法治化、国际化原则，朝着建设国际一流营商环境的目标不断前行。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,1,1,0),(230,'交通运输部：前三季度交通运输经济运行稳中有进','2019-10-26 22:47:32','<p class=\"otitle\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">（原标题：交通运输部：前三季度交通运输经济运行稳中有进 公路水路投资完成全年任务目标的92.9%）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">央广网北京10月24日消息(记者王子衿 张佳琪)今日(24日)，交通运输部召开例行发布会，新闻发言人、政策研究室主任吴春耕介绍，前三季度交通运输经济运行延续了上半年以来总体平稳、稳中有进的态势，投资规模保持高位运行，货运量、港口货物吞吐量较快增长，运输结构持续优化，主要指标保持在合理区间。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: initial; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: initial; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: initial; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: initial; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 700px; vertical-align: middle;\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/25/1bee9a267d2c48b9aec2f76bf1741417.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">图为发布会现场(央广网记者 王子衿 摄)</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">前三季度，交通固定资产投资规模保持高位运行，交通固定资产投资完成22918亿元，同比增长2.2%。其中，公路水路完成投资16713亿元、增长3.5%，完成全年任务目标的92.9%、进度同比加快1.1个百分点。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">在客运方面，前三季度，中国完成营业性客运量133.4亿人，同比下降1.6%。分方式看，铁路、民航客运量均保持较快增长。小客车出行持续旺盛，高速公路小客车流量同比增长8.5%。36个中心城市完成公共交通客运量500.4亿人，同比增长3.3%，其中轨道交通客运量增长13%。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">此外，前三季度中国完成营业性货运量389亿吨，同比增长5.9%。其中，公路、水路货运量分别增长5.7%和6.7%，均持续保持在较快增长区间。全国港口完成货物吞吐量103亿吨，同比增长5.2%，其中内、外贸分别增长5.8%和4%。集装箱吞吐量完成1.95亿标箱，增长4.8%。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">发布会上，吴春耕还介绍了前三季度交通运输行业经济运行中呈现的诸多亮点。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">重大项目建设方面，北京大兴国际机场正式投运，提前完成“十三五”新改建农村公路100万公里等任务目标。运输结构调整方面，出行和物流进一步向高铁、民航、高速公路、城市轨道交通等便捷高效舒适出行方式集聚，“公转铁”“公转水”工作有序推进，铁路、水路货运量同比分别增加1.8亿吨和3.4亿吨。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">此外，在服务水平提升方面，前三季度降低物流成本570亿元，取消高速公路省界收费站取得明显进展，工程建设加快推进，ETC发行任务完成率超过70%。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,1,1,0),(231,'跻身前40！中国营商环境全球排名再度提升','2019-10-26 22:48:05','<p class=\"otitle\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">（原标题：跻身前40！中国营商环境全球排名再度提升）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">新华社北京10月24日电（记者韩洁、于佳欣）世界银行于北京时间24日上午发布《全球营商环境报告2020》，中国营商环境全球排名继去年从此前78位跃至46位，今年再度升至第31位，跻身全球前40，连续两年入列全球优化营商环境改善幅度最大的十大经济体。</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img align=\"center\" id=\"{76A3CA7E-052D-48C6-9503-0465475E02B5}\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: initial; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: initial; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: initial; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: initial; display: block; height: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/24/6e261898edea4f288e0f8ab60ff7c3cd.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">“中国为改善中小企业的国内营商环境做出了巨大努力，保持了积极的改革步伐，在多项营商环境指标上取得了令人赞许的进步。”世界银行中国局局长芮泽说。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">世界银行自2003年起每年发布全球营商环境报告，选取10项评估指标对全球190个经济体的营商环境评分排名。该报告评估样本为各国常住人口最多的城市，其中11个人口过亿国家选择两个常住人口最多城市评估。2018年起，报告评估期调整为上年5月至次年5月。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">今年中国的营商环境评估在满分100分中得分77.9，世行打分依据是北京、上海两市及有关部门于2018年5月2日至2019年5月1日推出的优化营商环境改革措施，中国有9个指标领域的改革举措获世行认定，其中8项指标排名上升。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">以办理建筑许可为例，中国全球排名从去年的121位跃升至33位，提升了88位，京沪两市推出的简易低风险建筑项目免于环评备案改革、建立分类监管和审批制度及压缩供排水报装时间等改革举措，推动两地平均办理建筑许可全流程耗时缩至111天，获该指标质量指数满分15分，高于东亚地区132天和9.4分的平均水平。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">根据报告，中国保护中小投资者指标全球排名比去年提升36位至第28位，办理破产排名提升10位至第51位，跨境贸易排名提升9位至第56位，纳税排名提升9位至第105位，获得电力提升2位至第12位，执行合同排名提升1位至第5位，开办企业排名提升1位至第27位。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">据介绍，按照党中央、国务院决策部署，今年以来，国务院有关部门和京沪两市政府对标国际先进水平，迄今已推出130余项相关改革举措，进一步增强了我国营商环境的国际竞争力。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,1,3,1,0),(232,'多部门：从严规范房地产、汽车融资担保业务','2019-10-26 22:48:40','<p class=\"otitle\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">（原标题：多部门：从严规范房地产、汽车融资担保业务）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">人民网北京10月24日电 （申佳平）记者今日从银保监会官网获悉，为全面、深入贯彻实施《融资担保公司监督管理条例》》（下称《条例》），实现融资担保机构和融资担保业务监管全覆盖，中国银保监会会同发展改革委、工业和信息化部、财政部、住房和城乡建设部、农业农村部、商务部、人民银行、市场监管总局等融资性担保业务监管部际联席会议成员单位，联合印发了《关于印发融资担保公司监督管理补充规定的通知》（下称《补充规定》）。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">其中，从严规范融资担保业务牌照管理是主要内容之一。《补充规定》印发后，继续开展住房置业担保业务的住房置业担保公司（中心），应于2020年6月前向监督管理部门申领融资担保业务经营许可证，经营范围以监督管理部门批准文件为准，并接受监督管理部门的监管，严格执行《条例》及配套制度的监管要求。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">对于《补充规定》印发前发生的存量住房公积金贷款担保业务，可不计入融资担保责任余额，但应向监督管理部门单独列示报告。对有存量住房公积金贷款担保业务的住房置业担保公司（中心），监督管理部门可给予不同时限的过渡期安排，达标时限应不晚于2020年末。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">《补充规定》还指出，未经监督管理部门批准，汽车经销商、汽车销售服务商等机构不得经营汽车消费贷款担保业务，已开展的存量业务应当妥善结清；确有需要开展相关业务的，应当按照《条例》规定设立融资担保公司经营相关业务。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">在融资担保名称规范管理方面，《补充规定》强调，监督管理部门要会同市场监督管理部门做好辖内融资担保公司名称规范管理工作。融资担保公司的名称中应当标明融资担保字样；再担保公司应当标明融资再担保或融资担保字样；不持有融资担保业务经营许可证的公司，名称和经营范围中不得标明融资担保字样。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">此外，《融资担保责任余额计量办法》亦有相关补充修改。具体修改包括：“第四条 融资担保公司应当按照本办法的规定计量和管理融资担保责任余额。本办法中的净资产应当根据融资担保公司非合并财务报表计算。”</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">“第六条 单户在保余额500万元人民币以下且被担保人为小微企业的借款类担保业务权重为75%。单户在保余额200万元人民币以下且被担保人为农户的借款类担保业务权重为75%。为支持居民购买住房的住房置业担保业务权重为30%。住房置业担保业务仅包括住房公积金贷款担保业务和银行个人住房贷款担保业务。”</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">“第十一条 借款类担保责任余额=单户在保余额500万元人民币以下的小微企业借款类担保在保余额×75%+单户在保余额200万元人民币以下的农户借款类担保在保余额×75%+住房置业担保在保余额×30%+其他借款类担保在保余额×100%。”</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">银保监会方面表示，《补充规定》保持与现有法规相衔接，坚持从严监管，要求融资担保公司监督管理部门承担主体监管责任，将未取得融资担保业务经营许可证但实际上经营融资担保业务的住房置业担保公司、信用增进公司等机构纳入监管，结合实际分类处置，推进牌照管理工作，妥善结清不持牌机构的存量业务，有利于进一步规范融资担保经营行为，促进融资担保行业稳健运行，更好支持普惠金融发展。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,1,1,0),(233,'2019一带一路人文历史摄影展在京举行','2019-10-26 22:49:10','<p class=\"otitle\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">（原标题：2019一带一路人文历史摄影展在京举行）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">本报北京10月11日电 由人民日报社主办，故宫博物院协办，人民日报文化传媒有限公司、《国家人文历史》杂志社、人民日报一带一路文化中心共同承办的2019“一带一路”人文历史摄影展11日在故宫博物院开幕。第十一届全国人大常委会副委员长陈至立，人民日报社总编辑庹震，中国人民对外友好协会原会长陈昊苏，文化和旅游部党组成员、故宫博物院院长王旭东，人民日报社副总编辑张首映，中国文学艺术界联合会党组成员、副主席、书记处书记李前光，中国宋庆龄基金会党组书记、常务副主席杭元祥等出席开幕式。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">此次摄影展旨在通过一幅幅摄影作品，展现“一带一路”沿线国家和地区的经济社会发展情况和人文历史风貌。展览历时半年筹备，共收到投稿作品两万余幅。经过专家评审，从内容及形式等角度综合论证，精选出253幅作品参与展览，既有职业摄影师的精品力作，也有许多普通百姓的旅拍瞬间。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">摄影展分为“长风万里”“天涯比邻”“心同理同”“你好丝路”“不止所见”五大主题单元，既生动展现了“一带一路”沿线国家多姿多彩的人文风貌和众多古城遗址，又鲜活反映了中国人民与“一带一路”沿线人民互鉴互助互利的友好交流。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,1,3,1,0),(234,'【70年70城】记住德阳！在这里，被誉为“中国机长的摇篮”','2019-10-26 22:49:43','<p class=\"otitle\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">（原标题：【70年70城】记住德阳！在这里，被誉为“中国机长的摇篮”）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">\r\n\t\r\n\t</p><div class=\"video-wrapper\" style=\"background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(245, 245, 245); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"video-inner\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 25px; padding-top: 25px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"video\" style=\"background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; max-height: 450px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;\"><video width=\"100%\" style=\"height: 100%; max-height: 450px;\" preload=\"auto\" controls=\"controls\" poster=\"http://videoimg.nos-jd.163yun.com/cmssnapshot/20191011/msKS62658_0.jpg\">您的浏览器暂时无法播放此视频.</video>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"video-info clearfix\" style=\"clear: both; height: 20px; line-height: 20px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"fn-right\" style=\"float: right; font-size: 12px; height: 22px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"video-title\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); float: left; text-align: right; width: 300px;\" href=\"http://v.163.com/static/3/VKQ96VO37.html\" target=\"_blank\">【70年70城】记住德阳！在这里，被誉为“中国机长的摇篮”</a>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"video-from\" style=\"color: rgb(167, 167, 167); margin-left: 10px;\">（来源：网易政务）</span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"video-list\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"clearfix\" style=\"clear: both; height: 0px; list-style: outside none none; margin: 0px; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; width: 540px;\"><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\t\t\t\t\t</li></ul>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t</div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">\r\n\t\t</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">新中国成立70年来，作为长江文明之源的德阳，逢历史机遇、担强国重任，由一个西部农业小县，迅速成长为中国重大技术装备制造业基地和四川区域中心城市，地区生产总值长期稳居四川第三。进入新时代，德阳主动担负起“打造世界级重大装备制造基地”等重大历史使命，着力打造装备智造之都、改革开放高地、古蜀文化名城、美丽幸福家园“四张名片”。“人民记忆：70年70城”记住德阳，跟随六位行业代表人物，从中国机长、大国重器、中国智造、中国名片、大爱无疆、文化自信等方面，全面展现了德阳与新中国在时代发展的潮流中共同成长的光辉历程。德阳也必将在实现“两个一百年”奋斗目标和中华民族伟大复兴中国梦的历史进程中，谱写更加浓墨重彩的“德阳篇章”。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,1,6,1,0),(241,'联播+| 区块链与民生有何关联？习近平以四要擘画','2019-10-26 23:06:10','<p class=\"otitle\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">联播+10月24日，中共中央政治局首次就区块链技术发展现状和趋势进行集体学习。习近平总书记用四个“要”为区块链技术如何给社会发展带来实质变化指明方向。科学技术从来没有像今天这样深刻影响着国家前途命运，从来没有像今天这样深刻影响着人民生活福祉。央视网特梳理这四个“要”点，邀请您一起来学习。</span></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img width=\"355\" height=\"493\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"联播+| 区块链与民生有何关联？习近平以四要擘画\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/431117ea9dbc4153885be0397a381895.png\"/></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img width=\"360\" height=\"471\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"联播+| 区块链与民生有何关联？习近平以四要擘画\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/8277019ebf7b427795ca3827f286a5fa.png\"/></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img width=\"373\" height=\"509\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"联播+| 区块链与民生有何关联？习近平以四要擘画\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/eb736e56916a4026aa254eeefc71752d.png\"/></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img width=\"369\" height=\"487\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\" alt=\"联播+| 区块链与民生有何关联？习近平以四要擘画\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/26/e8a556e5d6174797b7be45c3b845bf0f.png\"/></p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,1,1,8,1,1);
INSERT INTO `t_news` VALUES (242,'河南一副县长直播卖货成网红 半小时成交近3000单','2019-10-27 16:42:53','<p class=\"otitle\" style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">（原标题：河南一副县长直播卖货成网红，半小时成交近3000单）</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">“我手里的这两个桃子是不是一个品种，有没有宝宝能答得上来，第一个答上来的，我送他一份礼品。”</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">这里是河南省南阳市镇平县马庄乡小碾王村的桃园。镇平县副县长王洪涛拿着黄桃，对着手机另外一头的网友如上说道。黄桃是刚从果园摘下来的。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">这不是王洪涛第一次直播。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">作为副县长，王洪涛思考如何带动村里扶贫。电商是个契机。电商发展，直播卖货受到商户和消费者的青睐。王洪涛2017年起尝试为村民及农副产品代言，进行直播卖货。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">效果最好的一次是，他直播刚开始半个小时，就收到近3000个预订黄桃的订单。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">新京报记者在王洪涛开设的直播账号内看到，平时他经常会通过直播或分享短视频的方式，介绍县里生产的面条、土鸡蛋等。在他最近一次直播河南省商务厅与电商平台共同举办的“农民丰收节”中，有70000余人次观看，累计进行过17场直播。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">因为直播，王洪涛被许多网友称为“网红县长”、“最接地气县长”。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">王洪涛说，不只他通过代言带动农民增收，镇平县县长此前也参与其中，曾直播2小时就帮村民卖出60万元的农产品。“2018年镇平县成功脱贫，电商扶贫起到很大作用。”</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-align: center; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"vertical-align: top; border: 0px; max-width: 550px;\" alt=\"河南一副县长直播卖货成网红 半小时成交近3000单\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/27/eab740f4b62743e9bf84f9fd07ad1c2f.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\"/><br/></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-align: center; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">河南镇平县副县长王洪涛和其他人一起直播销售画面，并在现场煮面。手机截图</span></p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">副县长为村民代言直播卖货</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">新京报：一开始怎么想到通过直播为农户代言的？</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">王洪涛：镇平县是国家级贫困县，有电商平台为了支持我们县脱贫，启动“村播行动”，通过县里“村播达人”介绍农产品，帮忙把农产品卖出去。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">我觉得我们作为县里干部，可以给大家做代言人，另外，感觉直播的效果会比传统电商好，因为能够让消费者更直观形象地感受到产品的特性。2017年起，我通过网络平台直播卖货。后来感觉效果挺好的，今年8月左右，我自己在淘宝上也申请开了个直播间。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">新京报：你直播一般都卖些什么？</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">王洪涛：主要直播卖当地农副产品，特别是支持贫困户参与的合作社企业的产品。比如土鸡蛋、荷叶茶、锦鲤、桃子等。我们当地的桃子、土鸡蛋等都是绿色无公害的。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">除了农副产品，有时看到镇平有成为旅游景点潜力的地方，我也会顺手拍下来，供网友欣赏，这些内容可能可以招来开发商或者是游客。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">新京报：通常会在什么时候做直播？</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">王洪涛：我本人分管县里的商务工作，有很多机会去调研、和老百姓做沟通。如果有合适的机会，我就会直播一会。我还会在下班后和周末做直播。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">新京报：平时用什么设备直播？</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">王洪涛：我一般拿个手机就直播或者拍摄视频了。今年丰收节，农产品准备好了，但是没有直播架。当时我们把手机放在茶杯上，靠在烧水壶上播放的。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">平时我都是很随意地给大家拍，比如拍一下果树的生长环境，树底下都是杂草，这是为了说明我们的果树没有用除草剂，我们拍摄这些只是希望让大家了解我们的农副产品是怎么生长形成的。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">工作之余开直播，个人未获利</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">新京报：有人反对你的直播代言吗？</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">王洪涛：刚开始有些声音，有些人觉得副县长开直播卖东西，和传统形象不符。但我负责全县商务工作，觉得自己应该对新的代言方式进行尝试，就坚持了下去。大家整体上都很支持。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">而且，之所以由我直播代言，一方面这块归我负责，另一方面现在为农副产品代言，对产品品质和安全性有背书，更有利于销售。我是副县长，我有义务和责任帮助老百姓把东西卖出去。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">新京报：之前你在河南电视台演播厅参加一项扶贫活动时向大家推介当地农副产品，有网友质疑你炒作，以直播代言的名义拿提成。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">王洪涛：我为当地农副产品代言，从来没有拿过提成或从中获利，全为公益行为。我可以理解群众的这些怀疑，但我觉得不从中拿提成这是我们作为一个政府官员的底线。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">新京报：直播代言变网红，对工作有影响吗？</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">王洪涛：我个人工作生活没太大的影响，不过成为网红不是我追求的。我希望通过这件事，带动更多人站出来帮村民的生产经营做点服务。之后如果他们有需要，我会继续做这个直播。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">新京报：县里其他人有这样做过吗？</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">王洪涛：去年第一次农民丰收节，我们通过竞争拿到了去杭州参加“首届丰收购物节”直播的资格。我们的艾进德县长带着县里的荷叶茶登上了晚会舞台，在短短两小时，销售额将近60万元，创造了镇平县农产品单品销售的最快速度记录。我们的县委书记还在中央电视台录播的一个活动中，给锦鲤做代言。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-weight: 700; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">直播带动贫困户脱贫</span></p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">新京报：直播效果挺好的吧，我看还有农户主动找你卖东西。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">王洪涛：对。2017年，有农户和我们说，因为阴雨天果园冬桃滞销。我们去看了，发现虽然卖相不好看，但品质还挺好的。之后我通过本地一个有影响力的自媒体公众号进行了直播。当时做了20分钟直播，直播后很快就有人过来采摘，还有些人在网上下订单，果园里桃子很快就卖完了。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">这件事之后，县里人通过各种途径联系我，说他们的东西很好，想让我看看。而且农户也开始尝试直播卖货。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">新京报：直播有给村里带来什么影响吗。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">王洪涛：直播带动了我们县里电商产业的升级。比如我们县里的侯集镇向寨村成为了全国第一个活物淘宝村，村里家家户户都在做金鱼养殖和电商销售工作，锦鲤通过电商直播已经卖向了全国。村里创建店铺200余个，订单累计达2.7万单，金鱼线上销售额从零突破2000余万元，带动268户贫困户增收。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">我们县现在有2个淘宝镇、9个淘宝村，先后两次被评为“国家级电子商务进农村示范县”，阿里研究院评估报告显示，我们县的电商发展指数位居南阳市第一位，是中西部大众电商创业最活跃县之一。</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">新京报：对接下来的电商有什么规划吗？</p><p style=\"margin: 28px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font: 400 16px/28px &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">王洪涛：2018年县里脱贫，离不开电商的帮助，我们在继续打造“电商+产业+农户”的经营模式，把县里人组织起来搞生产。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,10,1,0),(243,'公安厅原副厅长次子受审 现场画面曝光','2019-10-27 16:46:30','<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">原标题：公安厅原副厅长次子受审 现场画面曝光</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　撰文 | 余辉</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　落马近1年后，包头市纪委监委原副县级检查员孟根达来受审。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　他还有一个身份——<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(94, 111, 170); outline: none;\" href=\"https://news.sina.com.cn/c/2019-09-19/doc-iicezzrq6889687.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">内蒙古自治区公安厅原副厅长孟建伟</a>之子。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　据《内蒙古晨报》消息，2019年10月18日，鄂伦春自治旗人民法院以涉嫌利用影响力受贿罪，非法持有枪支、弹药罪对孟根达来公开开庭审理。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　现场画面也得以曝光。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　<strong style=\"font-weight: 700 !important;\">　政法系统工作多年</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　孟根达来，男，蒙古族，1981年8月出生，今年38岁，大学文化，2000年11月参加工作，2007年12月加入中国共产党，内蒙古包头人。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　他毕业于内蒙古自治区乌盟人民警察学校公安专业，落马前曾长期在政法系统工作。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　2000年11月，19岁的孟根达来到了内蒙古自治区卓资县公安局工作，4年后到包头市稀土高新区公安分局当科员。2年后晋升，成为稀土高新区公安分局网监大队大队长（副科级）。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　2009年11月，孟根达来离开公安系统，任包头市昆都仑区检察院纪检组长（正科级）。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　3年多后（2013年3月），他再度履新，成为昆都仑区检察院副检察长。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　2015年5月，孟根达来履新包头市检察院检察技术处处长，1年后调整为包头市纪委副县级检查员。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　2018年9月，孟根达来任包头市纪委监委驻市政协机关纪检监察组副县级检查员，不到两个月（2018年10月30日），孟根达来被留置。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　孟根达来被留置几天后，官方公布了他被查的消息。</p><div class=\"img_wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: top; display: block; max-width: 640px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/news/transform/697/w550h147/20191020/4c20-ihfpfvz8380799.png\" data-link=\"\" data-mceselected=\"1\" data-mcesrc=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/378/w929h249/20191020/354e-ihfpfvz8378243.png\"/></div><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　根据检方指控，孟根达来涉嫌利用影响力受贿罪，非法持有枪支、弹药罪。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　孟根达来利用其父亲孟建伟任包头市委常委、政法委书记兼公安局局长、内蒙古自治区公安厅副厅长的职权和地位形成的便利条件，为请托人孙某、曹某、王某谋取不正当利益，收受请托人200余万元人民币。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　妻子是交警支队办事员时，孟建伟是支队队长</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　在纪委的通报中，还有一人也被调查，即孟建伟妻子刘丽萍。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　刘丽萍，女，汉族，1953年12月出生，大专文化，1971年5月参加工作，1996年6月加入中国共产党，内蒙古磴口县人。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　刘丽萍的履历集中在乌海市公安局。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　对比简历，刘丽萍和孟建伟的首次交集，是在1990年。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　1990年7月，37岁的乌海市玻璃厂工人刘丽萍到了乌海市公安局交警支队当办事员，当时孟建伟的身份是乌海市交警支队队长。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　2003年6月，时任乌兰察布盟公安局局长的孟建伟履新包头市公安局局长。1年之后（2004年9月），刘丽萍到包头市公安局交警支队任主任科员，并在2008年12月退休。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　2018年10月31日，孟建伟落马。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　根据检方公开的消息，孟建伟涉嫌三罪——受贿罪，巨额财产来源不明罪，非法持有枪支、弹药罪。</p><div class=\"img_wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: top; display: block; max-width: 640px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/news/transform/116/w550h366/20191020/4f34-ihfpfvz8380919.jpg\" data-link=\"\" data-mceselected=\"1\" data-mcesrc=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/199/w1080h719/20191020/564a-ihfpfvz8378289.jpg\"/></div><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　其中，他敛财的第一个岗位，便是“包头市公安局长”——</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　“被告人孟建伟作为国家工作人员，利用先后担任包头市公安局长，包头市委常委、政法委书记，内蒙古自治区公安厅副厅长等职务的便利，索取或者非法收受他人财物，为他人谋取利益；利用本人职权或者地位形成的便利条件，通过其他国家工作人员职务上的行为，为请托人谋取不正当利益，索取请托人财物或者非法收受请托人财物，数额特别巨大”。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　更多的细节也得以披露。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　内蒙古纪委监委在《“伞”上之“伞”孟建伟》一文中披露，孟建伟在其任包头市委常委、政法委书记期间，指使妻子开奇石店，洗白违纪违法所得，同时千方百计敛财。黑社会组织头目郭某某就曾在该奇石店花数十万元高价购买奇石。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　<strong style=\"font-weight: 700 !important;\">　“我现在很悔恨”</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　上述文章还提到了孟建伟的两个儿子。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　2011年6月，1名涉嫌开设赌场罪犯罪嫌疑人通过孟建伟的大儿子办理取保候审后逃脱了后续的侦查和审判。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　孟建伟的二儿子生活奢靡，道德败坏，与社会闲散人员称兄道弟，帮人办事后心安理得地受贿，并非法持有枪支、弹药。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　据《中国新闻周刊》报道，孟建伟长子孟银柱也已经被抓。“孟银柱开设赌场，并利用其父影响力，成为很多赌场老板的靠山，并多次捞人。”</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　如今，孟根达来先于他的父亲，站在了法庭上。</p><div class=\"img_wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: top; display: block; max-width: 640px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/news/transform/115/w550h365/20191020/eaa7-ihfpfvz8381022.jpg\" data-link=\"\" data-mceselected=\"1\" data-mcesrc=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/198/w1080h718/20191020/d6ae-ihfpfvz8378290.jpg\"/></div><div class=\"otherContent_01\" id=\"ad_44086\" style=\"margin: 10px 20px 10px 0px; padding: 4px; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: block; float: left; overflow: hidden; clear: both; width: 336px; height: 280px;\"><ins class=\"sinaads sinaads-done\" id=\"Sinads49447\" style=\"display: block; overflow: hidden; text-decoration: none;\" data-ad-status=\"done\" data-ad-pdps=\"PDPS000000044086\"><ins style=\"text-decoration: none; margin: 0px auto; width: 336px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden; height: 280px;\"><br/></ins></ins></div><p class=\"show_author\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; text-align: right; color: rgb(77, 79, 83); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;\\\\5FAE软雅黑&quot;, SimSun, &quot;\\\\5B8B体&quot;, Arial; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><br/></p><p><br/></p>',1,'http://localhost:8080/news/File/a6f2-ihfpfvz8381205.jpg',0,1,12,1,1),(244,'英媒：越南人偷渡英国花费≈一越南农民30年收入','2019-10-27 19:39:48','<p class=\"otitle\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">（原标题：<span style=\"background-color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">英媒曝越南人偷渡英国</span>：一趟花费相当于一个越南农民30年收入）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img width=\"558\" height=\"315\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/27/ae95915eae1640d390e1c37c3301b46b.png\"/></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">失踪越南籍女子Pham Thi Tra My和越南籍男子Luong被曝可能是英国集装箱藏尸案的受害者</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">【环球网报道】英国集装箱藏尸案被曝死者可能有一部分来自越南，已有14个越南家庭报案称家庭成员疑似在英国失踪。英国广播公司(BBC)26日报道称，在重重谜团的背后，可能是人均单次可达近4万英镑(约合35万元人民币)的偷渡费用。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">英国广播公司(BBC)26日报道称，每年有约1.8万越南人偷渡到欧洲，目的是挣钱养家。根据联合国数据，越南移民每年付给人口走私犯的钱可能达到2.34亿英镑(约合21亿元人民币)。 \r\n反人口贩卖专家武女士(Mimi \r\nVu)介绍，偷渡费用因人而异。对于没什么钱的人来说，费用大致在7800~11600英镑左右(约7万~10万元人民币)，而这个“价位”的旅途会“更艰辛”，甚至可能会涉及夜间徒步穿越丛林;但较为富裕的人则可申请申根签证借道巴黎，大多是乘坐飞机，花费约在3万到3.9万英镑(约合27万~35万元人民币)。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">“但不管选择哪个‘级别’的‘服务’，你最后都只能躲在卡车或渡船里。”武女士介绍，有些越南人会选择途经中国、俄罗斯、波兰等国，甚至可能停留在“中转国”打工挣下一段路的旅费，或是为走私犯挣钱。而最后一站往往选在法国，偷渡客可以付钱让走私犯将他们藏在卡车货箱中而不被司机发现。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">“越南有着非常以家族为中心的文化，一切都是为了家人。”武女士表示，3万英镑相当于一名越南农民30年的收入，是个“天文数字”。为了支付这笔巨款，许多越南家庭甚至不惜变卖家产或借债。但他们相信这笔钱是值得的，“因为这可能是他们小孩争取光明前途的最佳途径。”</p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img width=\"558\" height=\"315\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; max-width: 550px; vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/10/27/b9a192c5846244d2b9f6800b12dad8d0.png\"/></p><p class=\"f_center\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">资料图：越南农民</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">BBC称，尽管越南经济发展迅速，总体减贫效果显著，但地区间的发展仍不均衡，存在巨大的劳动力过剩。武女士介绍说，“实际上，在从越南去往欧洲和英国的移民中，大多数都来自数得过来的几个省份”，而这些地区在过去数十年中一直有移民海外挣钱养家的传统。但是在英国，越南餐厅、美甲沙龙和非法大麻种植业等行业都对越南低端劳动力有着很大的需求。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">关于越南人为什么选择英国，牛津布鲁克斯大学政治社会学讲师塔姆辛?巴伯博士分析称，一方面偷渡者知道他们在英国很有可能会找到工作;另一方面，已经在英国工作生活的越南人可以在住宿和就业上提供帮助，他们已经形成了庞大的人脉网络。但是“对于越南低端劳动者，目前并没有合法的工作居留渠道”，偷渡是他们眼中“在海外挣钱的唯一机会”。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"></p><div class=\"gg200x300\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(229, 229, 229); color: rgb(64, 64, 64); float: left; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 0; margin: 0px 40px 0px 0px; overflow: hidden; padding: 19px; position: relative; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><div id=\"ssp_6374560\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;\"></div><a class=\"ad_hover_href\" style=\"background: url(&quot;&amp;quot;https://yt-adp.ws.126.net/channel4/ad_3017_ajgf_20190221.png&amp;quot;&quot;) 0% 0% / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box transparent; bottom: 0px; color: rgb(15, 107, 153); height: 17px; left: 0px; position: absolute; text-decoration-line: underline; width: 30px; z-index: 10;\" href=\"http://\" target=\"_self\"></a></div><p style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 32px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 32px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">当地时间23日，英国警方在英格兰东南部埃塞克斯郡一个工业园区内的一辆集装箱货车里发现39具尸体，货车司机莫里斯?罗宾逊当日被警方拘捕。据英国《卫报》26日报道，英国警方当天宣布，英国检察机关已经授权警方以过失杀人罪、串谋贩运人口、串谋协助非法移民和洗钱等39项罪名起诉罗宾逊。同日，越南总理阮春福下令调查此事，并命令警方对疑似人口贩运活动展开调查。英国埃塞克斯郡警方表示，目前他们获得了大量越南籍民众关于他们失踪亲属的报告和线索。尽管目前不能完全确定遇难者身份，但英国警方接下来的调查重点将转向越南社区，同时也不能排除有其他国籍遇难者的可能性。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,16,1,1),(245,'定了！2019年合肥工大这么干！','2019-10-30 08:15:53','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">2月22日至23日，合肥工业大学召开寒假工作研讨会。</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　<img src=\"http://spider.ws.126.net/33627bc52642b280e3cce884dbac3140.jpeg\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 20px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\"/><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/> <br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> 会议主题 &nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　以习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想和党的十九大精神为指导，深入贯彻落实全国教育大会精神和本科教育工作会议精神，加强党对学校工作的全面领导，落实立德树人根本任务，全面推进学校内涵发展，确保党中央、教育部和安徽省委省政府各项工作部署在学校落地生根，以优异成绩庆祝建国70周年。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> 集体学习 &nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　会议集体学习了习近平总书记在省部级主要领导干部专题研讨班开班式上重要讲话精神，传达学习了中共中央政治局常委、中央书记处书记王沪宁在第26次全国高校党的建设工作会议上的讲话精神，2019年全国教育工作会议和教育部直属高校工作咨询委员会第28次会议精神，以及安徽省委坚持底线思维着力防范化解重大风险专题培训班精神。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> 深入研讨 &nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　会议紧密结合新形势新任务新要求和工作实际，按照学校第八次党代会确定的目标任务及学校“十三五”事业发展规划要求，深入研讨以下主要内容：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　贯彻落实全国教育工作会议精神，大力加强科学管理，以一流本科教育和“双一流”建设为牵引，深入推进人才培养、学科建设、科学研究等工作，不断提升学校办学质量和发展水平；</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　贯彻落实全国高校思想政治工作会议精神，发挥教师党支部的组织育人功能，实施“教师党支部建设之课程思政”项目；</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　贯彻落实全国教育大会精神，完善人才培养体系，实施“‘两张成绩单’建设，完善德智体美劳全面发展的人才培养体系”项目，聚焦能力导向一体化教育教学体系建设、“新工科”内涵建设等。</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　<img src=\"http://spider.ws.126.net/e6d822c7e0d83b0b13e474e67660c4e4.jpeg\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 20px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\"/><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/> <br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">校党委副书记、校长梁樑</strong>在会上深刻分析了学校面临的新形势新任务和新要求，对本科教学、研究生培养、科学研究、师资队伍建设以及课程思政等方面作出全面部署。梁樑指出，学校深入研究发展中面临的各种挑战与问题，紧抓重点领域、关键环节、主要矛盾，将实施<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">教师党支部建设之“课程思政”</strong>和<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">“两张成绩单”</strong>建设作为学校2019年两项重点工作。全校各单位要坚持问题导向、科学系统谋划，切实将思想和行动统一到校党委的决策部署上来，团结带领全校师生员工全力落实好2019年各项工作。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　梁樑强调，培养德智体美劳全面发展的社会主义建设者和接班人是高等院校最重要的使命和职责。近年来，学校高度重视人才培养工作，“立德树人、能力导向、创新创业”集成教育教学体系已经形成，但在课程体系、过程管理、质量保证等环节仍有待进一步完善优化。全校各单位要深刻理解“德智体美劳”的丰富内涵，以制定2019版本科和研究生专业指导性教学计划为抓手，紧扣全面提高人才培养质量这一核心点，坚持教师和学生两个中心并重，强化过程管理，严格教学纪律，重塑教育教学体系，确保实现“培养德才兼备，能力卓越，自觉服务国家的骨干与领军人才”的人才培养总目标。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　梁樑强调，要强化价值引领，进一步明确教师开展科学研究的价值导向，提高教学质量和加强学生创新能力的培养，不断提升承担国家重点重大项目和服务地方社会经济发展的能力，努力在解决国家重大需求的高水平科研成果上取得新的突破。各单位负责同志要勇于担当，全身心投入，结合本单位工作实际，科学制定工作方案，认真落实学校决策部署，推动学校高质量内涵式发展。</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　<img src=\"http://spider.ws.126.net/c2033eeace11a7ec28558d8f09466ecb.jpeg\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 20px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\"/><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/> <br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">校党委书记余其俊</strong>在总结讲话中指出，为国家培养更多德才兼备，能力卓越，自觉服务国家的骨干与领军人才，是新时代赋予学校的历史责任。近年来，学校在人才培养、科学研究、学科建设、国际交流与合作、文化传承等方面都取得了长足发展。此次工作研讨会目标明确、针对性强，与会同志调研充分、研讨深入，研讨发言紧扣内涵式发展，坚持问题导向，分析存在问题、厘清发展思路、提出措施对策、谋划硬招实招，对推进学校2019年各项工作具有重要参考意义。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　余其俊强调，2019年，全校各单位要科学谋划、认真组织实施教师党支部建设之“课程思政”工作，切实发挥教师党支部的组织育人功能，真正形成全员全过程全方位育人思想政治工作新局面；</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　要加强“两张成绩单”建设实施计划，完善德智体美劳全面发展的人才培养体系；</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　要进一步健全完善相关制度，始终把规矩挺在前面，遵规律谋发展，在守纪律、讲规矩的前提下，大力支持党员干部、师生员工为学校事业发展而努力拼搏；</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　要坚持师德师风第一标准，全面加强教师队伍建设，着力打造政治素质过硬、业务能力精湛、育人水平高超的高素质教师队伍；</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　要持续不断地坚决反对“四风”，进一步营造向上向善的政治生态，进一步树正气、讲团结，弘扬主旋律、激发正能量；</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　要建立健全党政干部容错纠错机制，切实支持想干事、能干事、干成事的干部放手大胆为学校工作，为他们保驾护航，大力营造改革创新、担当作为、干事创业的良好氛围。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　余其俊强调，学校各级领导干部要自觉以习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想为指导，进一步提高政治站位，树牢“四个意识”，坚定“四个自信”，坚决做到“两个维护”，坚持底线思维，增强风险防范意识，强化安全稳定红线意识，层层落实责任，切实抓好安全稳定工作，保障学校各项事业发展稳步向前。要进一步学习贯彻落实全国高校思想政治工作会议、全国教育大会精神，认真领会、坚决落实学校近期及远期各项工作部署，结合各单位实际，迅速制定工作方案和时间表，全力推进2019年学校各项工作，以优异成绩迎接建国70周年。</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://spider.ws.126.net/d895b65d90613a0dd5bbe82f5a3da040.jpeg\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 20px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;\"/><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/> <br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　会上，校党委副书记陈刚、副校长陈鸿海先后就发挥教师党支部组织育人功能、推进课程思政建设，第二课堂成绩单建设作主题发言。校党委副书记、纪委书记陆林，副校长刘晓平、刘志峰，总会计师闫平，副校长季益洪就各自分管工作作主题发言。教务处处长陈翌庆、体育部主任柴业宏就两张成绩单培养德智体美劳全面发展本科人才和2019年学校体育工作改革方案作主题发言。仪器科学与光电工程学院党委书记钟军、电气与自动化工程学院院长丁立健分别就分组讨论情况作了汇报发言。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;\">　　全体校领导，党委常委，校长助理，各党群部门主要负责人，各行政部门正处级领导干部，学术委员会秘书长，各学院党政主要负责人，各直附属单位党政负责人参加会议。</p><p><br/></p>',1,'http://localhost:8080/news/File/33627bc52642b280e3cce884dbac3140.jpeg.jpg',0,0,5,6,0),(246,'多家媒体刊文评合工大举报事件：真相不能靠自查','2019-10-30 08:17:08','<p style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><strong>光明网评论合工大“副校长举报校长”事件真相不能校内博弈</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">合肥工业大学副校长朱大勇实名举报校长梁樑弄虚作假一事又有了最新进展。8月5日下午，朱大勇表示，校党委在4日下午6时召开了常委会，会后合肥工业大学党委副书记、纪委书记陆林代表校党委向他通报了会议意见：校党委要求其立即书面检讨举报内容、方式，立即停止传播，立即主动消除负面影响。以上三点需在两天内完成，否则建议教育部严肃处理他。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">三个“立即”，两天完成，不然，告诉“家长”去。可问题是，合肥工业大学副校长朱大勇实名举报校长梁樑弄虚作假一事，仅凭“合肥工业大学新闻中心”的一纸否认式说明，真相就水落石出、板上钉钉了吗？</p><p style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">常理上说，都是文化人，断不至于一言不合就实名诬告。尤为值得注意的是：合工大是教育部直属院校，也是一所国内知名的工科院校，而副校长公开实名举报校长的行为，本身就殊为少见。这个时候，校方急吼吼就要盖棺定论，既没有令人信服的反驳证明、也未经主管部门铿锵发声，尤其是对待举报人的姿态，起码不太契合高教深改语境下重点院校的法治作为。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">朱大勇的举报，分成三个层面：比如职务便利、比如校区调整，但这两个方面要佐证违规与否，三言两语还真不太容易说得清；倒是其中一点，是可以真假立辨的——在朱大勇的举报信中，还有个主要问题是梁樑获得“第四届全国教育改革创新杰出校长奖”一事。朱大勇称，梁樑的报奖材料多处造假，“效果亮点”中列出的成果绝大多数与他毫不沾边。例如，材料中提到“2013年以来，在校生在省部级以上竞赛中获奖1500余项”，而2013年梁樑还在中国科技大学。那么，究竟是朱大勇以讹传讹还是梁樑弄虚作假，把申报材料“牵出来溜溜”，不都一目了然了吗？既然有白纸黑字，何必呈口舌之快而互撕？</p><p style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">不是公众盼着合工大出事，也不是大家对朱大勇情有独钟，只是，对于一个级别不低的文化人的实名举报、对于学术领域不可草率的中国高校来说，“合工大事件”恐怕不宜草草收场，或者说，在程序正义上不能漏洞百出。第一，此事真相已经不适合校内博弈。正如媒体所说的，一名教育部部属大学正职领导是否涉嫌违纪违法的判定问题，在于教育部和中央纪委驻教育部纪检组、监察局。适格主体的严肃问题，不是谁都能说了算的封口问题。第二，校方的一纸说明反而是“说而不明”。所谓均与事实不符，那么，这算不算举报人无中生有？否认容易，证据与逻辑在哪里？就像举报人说的，“我是实名举报，如果学校纪委给出结论，我还可以反馈。反馈不行的话，我还可以向上级机构举报，再进行核实。程序还没有走完，就开始匆匆忙忙地要打击报复我。”</p><p style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">既然彼此都承认“毫无私人恩怨”，既然纠葛的又都是合工大清誉攸关的议题，还是摆到桌面上、摊在阳光下辩白清楚为好。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">用顶层设计的话说，办好中国特色社会主义大学，要坚持和完善党委领导下的校长负责制。不过，一把手权力过大、荣誉过于归拢集中的乱象，恐怕也正是眼下高校深改的核心课题。让校长的归校长、学校的归学校，个人和集体不要痴缠在一起，权力与利益不要混杂在一起，这是“合工大事件”最大的启示。至于事件本身的是非曲折，学校的面子再大，恐怕也大不过遮无可遮的真相吧。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><strong>法制晚报：副校长举报校长岂能由高校自查？</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">合肥工业大学副校长朱大勇实名举报校长梁樑弄虚作假一事正在发酵。8月4日,合肥工业大学官网挂出一则情况通报,对副校长举报校长一事作出回应称,校长梁樑的参评申报材料中未发现有虚假内容,举报材料中多个问题均与事实不符。(8月5日《新京报》)</p><p style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">大学在职副校长实名举报自己的顶头上司校长,这样的举动实属罕见。然而,当所有人都将目光聚焦在副校长举报校长事件本身时,却忽略了一个关键问题,就是不管副校长举报校长内容是否属实,也不论副校长举报校长出于何种目的,这件事情都不该由合工大自己调查。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">首先,梁樑以合工大校长身份申报参评“全国教育改革创新杰出校长奖”,意味着这不是一种个人行为,而是一项职务行为,代表的是合工大这所高校,申报材料中盖有合工大的印章。换言之,梁樑弄虚作假,实质上也表示合工大弄虚作假。现在让高校自己调查,高校怎么可能承认自己弄虚作假?其次,合工大是一所教育部直属高校,校长、副校长都是教育部部管干部,由教育部直接任命。现在由合工大的纪委调查校长有没有在申报材料中弄虚作假行为,实质上是下级调查上级,既没有管辖权限,调查结论也很难有说服力。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">综上可见,对于合工大副校长举报校长在申报材料中弄虚作假一事,不该由合工大自行调查,这样的调查结论也没有公信力。要确保调查结论的可信度,应当由“全国教育改革创新杰出校长奖”活动的主办方亲自调查,给出调查结论,并根据结论进行处理,确认被举报的校长有资格获得这份荣誉,或撤销先前授予的荣誉,这也是活动主办方维护活动公信力的必由之路。另一方面,合工大校长作为教育部部管干部,对于被举报存在的弄虚作假以及其他行为,教育部应当尽快介入调查,并及时公开调查结论。</p>',0,NULL,0,0,1,6,0),(247,'安徽14市PM2.5浓度降幅仍未达标 特别是皖北4市','2019-10-30 08:18:00','<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">新安晚报 安徽网 大皖客户端讯&nbsp; 10月29日，安徽省生态环境厅发布今年以来全省大气污染防治攻坚行动有关情况，虽然全省大气环境质量在持续改善，但形势依然严峻。截至10月28日，全省14个未达标城市（除黄山、池州）PM2.5平均浓度为44.9微克/立方米，同比下降2%，但降幅仍未达标，特别是皖北4市的PM2.5平均浓度普遍处于高位。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">为了加强全省大气污染防治工作，今年以来省生态环境厅启动强化督查，完成了2018年至2019年度秋冬季攻坚目标任务。2018年10月1日至2019年3月31日，全省PM2.5平均浓度为63.9微克/立方米，比2017年至2018年度秋冬季下降8.2%，重污染天数较同期减少52天，圆满完成攻坚目标。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">根据国家约束性指标要求，今年我省14个未达标城市PM2.5平均浓度较2015年需下降14.4%，但目前仅比2015年同期下降13.3%；皖北4市（亳州、阜阳、淮北、宿州）PM2.5平均浓度普遍处于高位，改善成效不明显。此外，煤炭消费总量不降反升，运输结构调整仍然滞后，今年上半年“公转铁”进展较慢，铁路占比仅为1.96%，运输结构仍然不优。秸秆焚烧屡禁不止，六安等市秸秆禁烧反弹明显，特别是近日被生态环境部通报。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">为确保实现国家下达的空气质量改善目标，我省将加快推进钢铁行业超低排放改造、工业炉窑综合整治、挥发性有机物深度治理、燃煤锅炉淘汰等主要工作，并做好秋冬季大气污染综合防治。此外，我省还将持续开展大气污染强化监督帮扶，对空气质量改善落后的、重点任务推进缓慢的进行约谈问责。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">新安晚报 安徽网 大皖客户端记者 姚一鸣</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,2,6,0),(248,'2019年国家森林城市拟批准名单公示 安徽这3个城市入围','2019-10-30 08:18:30','<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">安徽网、大皖客户端讯 10月21日，国家林业和草原局发出《关于2019年国家森林城市拟批准名单的公示》，该公示文件显示，国家林业和草原局拟批准28个城市为国家森林城市，其中包括安徽省马鞍山市、淮北市和宿州市，公示时间为2019年10月21日—2019年10月25日。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">此次国家森林和草原局拟批准的国家森林城共28个：北京市延庆区，河北省唐山市，保定市和廊坊市，吉林省敦化市，江苏省盐城市，浙江省东阳市和永康市，安徽省马鞍山市，淮北市和宿州市，福建省南平市，宁德市和平潭综合实验区，山东省胶州市，河南省安阳市和信阳市，湖北省荆州市和恩施市，广东省汕头市和梅州市，广西壮族自治区防城港市，四川省眉山市，云南省曲靖市和景洪市，陕西省榆林市，汉中市和商洛市。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">“国家森林城市”是国家对一个城市在生态环境建设方面最高的评价。<span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">目前，安徽已创建国家森林城市10个、省级森林城市52个、省级森林城镇522个、省级森林村庄3966个。安徽将进一步加快城乡绿化步伐，构筑生态保护绿色屏障，促进绿色富民，提升城市乡村的生态服务功能和文化品位。</span></p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,2,6,0),(249,'长三角高铁沿线外部环境隐患集中整治大会战全面启动','2019-10-30 08:19:15','<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">安徽网&nbsp;大皖客户端讯&nbsp;记者中国铁路上海局集团有限公司获悉，根据国家铁路集团有限公司的部署要求，长三角铁路自即日起至2020年1月10日，开展高铁沿线外部环境隐患集中整治大会战，为2020年春运创造良好的铁路外部安全环境。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">据悉，此次集中整治大会战，中国铁路上海局集团有限公司将会同地方政府、铁路公安联合推进，排查整治五个方面的安全隐患。一是高铁用地范围内的环境安全隐患，重点是铁路用地红线范围内的违法建筑、违法侵占、违法经营等行为；二是铁路线路安全保护区内的环境安全隐患，重点是安保区内非法建(构)筑物、取土、挖沙、挖沟、堆放悬挂物品等违法行为，以及违法侵占带来的安全风险；三是铁路线路安全保护区外的环境安全隐患，重点是不满足安全防护距离要求的易燃易爆品、影响线路基础稳定的施工作业、违法取水、采矿等各类违法行为，以及高铁沿线两侧可能被大风刮上铁路的彩钢板、防尘网、塑料大棚等飘浮物隐患；四是高铁沿线道路、水路、管线路安全隐患，重点对“公跨铁”立交桥和公铁并行地段的安全防护设施隐患、非法下穿铁路路基、桥涵的油(燃)气管线;五是消除铁路内部建构筑物、防护设施隐患。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">目前，长三角高铁沿线外部环境安全隐患集中排查已全面展开，铁路部门坚持边查边改的原则，依法依规同步开展整治工作。同时，中国铁路上海局集团有限公司将建立健全政府有关部门、铁路公安机关和铁路单位有效联动的综合治理工作体系和长效机制，对高铁沿线影响铁路运输安全的风险实施有效管控。&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">许文峰&nbsp;新安晚报&nbsp;安徽网&nbsp;大皖客户端记者&nbsp;&nbsp;刘旸</p>',0,NULL,0,0,13,1,0),(250,'芜湖发布2名干部任前公示 陈蓉拟任市纪委常委','2019-10-30 08:19:57','<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">安徽网、大皖客户端讯 据芜湖先锋网消息，为在干部选拔任用工作中进一步扩大民主，广泛听取群众意见，把干部选好、选准，根据《党政领导干部选拔任用工作条例》规定，对以下拟任人选进行公示：</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">陈 &nbsp;蓉，女，汉族，1968年8月出生，籍贯、出生地安徽池州，在职大学学历，中共党员，现任市监察委员会委员，拟任市纪委常委。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">王成权，男，汉族，1970年7月出生，籍贯、出生地安徽庐江，全日制大学学历、医学学士，中共党员，现任市纪委第五纪检监察室主任，拟任市监察委员会委员。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">如有情况需要反映的，请于2019年10月29日至11月4日向市委组织部干部监督科（举报中心）口头、书面或通过举报网站反映（电话：0553-12380；短信举报号码：05534712380；举报网站网址：www.wuhu12380.gov.cn）。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">接待时间：上午8:00—12:00，下午2：30—5:30</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">意见箱设在市委组织部门口。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">我们将严格遵守党的纪律，履行保密义务。为便于对反映的问题进行调查核实，请在反映问题时，提供具体事实或线索，并请提供联系方式，以便我们将核实情况作反馈。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: right; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">中共芜湖市委组织部</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: right; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">2019年10月28日</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,3,6,0),(251,'合肥地铁新动向：5号线好消息频传 顺利下穿1号线','2019-10-30 08:21:57','<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">新安晚报&nbsp; 安徽网&nbsp; 大皖客户端讯 日前，合肥市轨道交通5号线祁门路站-高铁南站区间右线盾构机顺利下穿1号线既有区间隧道，标志着该区间盾构施工两次下穿1号线既有区间隧道施工任务圆满完成。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">近期，5号线连续传出好消息，宁夏路站-庐州大道站盾构区间左线顺利贯通（盾构区间下穿了包河大道高架桥、许小河箱涵及多处管线等风险源）；祁门路站-桐城南路站盾构区间左线顺利贯通；祁门路站-高铁南站区间右线盾构机顺利下穿1号线既有区间隧道。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">其中，祁门路站-高铁南站盾构区间全长727.65米，盾构机从祁门路站始发，下穿1号线下行线隧道到达高铁南站，盾构机进行站内调头后，在高铁南站二次始发，再次下穿1号线下行线隧道，折返回祁门路站。盾构机掘进过程中，施工难度大，工艺工序复杂，施工风险和环境风险高，属一级风险。该区间左线盾构机已于6月29日顺利穿越1号线既有区间隧道。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">据介绍 ，该段盾构机下穿期间各参建单位24小时值班，根据盾构掘进工况和监测数据，组织专家分析总结，并做好各项应急措施。最终顺利完成省内首例以近距3.97米、危险源范围108.4米的难度下穿已投入运营的1号线下行线，成功保障了1号线安全运营和5号线隧道掘进安全，为盾构施工下穿已运营轨道交通线路等风险源积累了丰富经验。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">截至目前，轨道交通5号线全线已有27座车站、1明挖区间、2出入段线完成主体结构封顶；全线33台盾构机，已有28台盾构机下井，26台盾构机进行掘进施工，累计完成盾构总工程量的69.17%。&nbsp; <br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">新安晚报&nbsp; 安徽网&nbsp; 大皖客户端记者 伍静</p>',1,'http://localhost:8080/news/File/c013663c18753a2413a51c7ee725ab19.jpeg!w160_h110.jpg',0,0,6,6,0),(252,'合肥献血条例2020年施行：一次无偿献血 终身免费用血','2019-10-30 08:22:50','<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">新安晚报 安徽网 大皖客户端讯 《合肥市献血条例》将于明年元旦起施行，其中“一次无偿献血，终身免费用血”的规定备受关注。此前在合肥参加献血能享受这一政策吗？除此之外，献血者还能享受哪些优待？献血者如何进行血费报销？就此，记者昨日采访了合肥市中心血站负责人。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;\">所有献血者均享受新政策</strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">条例从明年元旦开始实施，那么此前在合肥参加无偿献血的献血者能享受“一次无偿献血，终身免费用血”的政策吗？</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">“从条例施行开始，所有献血者都可以享受新政策。”合肥市中心血站党委书记、站长胡晓玉表示，按照目前正在实施的无偿献血偿还政策，献血者本人临床用血时，按所献血量的两倍免费用血；本人献血量累计满1000毫升的，终身享受免费用血；献血者其配偶和直系亲属临床用血时，可以享受等量半费用血，该政策将延续至2019年12月31日。从2020年1月1日起，所有在合肥参加过无偿献血的献血者都可以享受“一次无偿献血，终身免费用血”的新政策。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;\">献血者或可享受更多优待</strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">除了“一次无偿献血，终身免费用血”，合肥市对献血者还会拿出哪些奖励政策？</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">记者注意到，在此前公布的《合肥市献血条例（草案）》中，曾对“献血待遇”作出规定：在本市献血5次以上的，献血者及其配偶和直系亲属每年可以免费游览政府投资主办的公园、旅游风景区等场所。在本市献血5次以上且捐献单采血小板2次以上的大中专院校学生，在本市就业后可以优先申请公共租赁住房。在本市献血10次以上的，献血者可以免交公立医疗机构普通门诊诊查费、免费乘坐城市公共汽车。荣获国家无偿献血奉献奖的献血者和无偿献血志愿服务终身荣誉奖的志愿者，在享受以上待遇的同时，还可以享受下列待遇：同等条件下优先提供就业岗位，优先推荐就业，优先保障子女入托、入学；免费乘坐城市轨道交通；在政府投资的公共停车场和路内停车位每天免费连续停放3小时；对符合条件的就业困难人员给予相应社保补贴。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">胡晓玉透露，目前具体的奖励细则正在制订当中，此前草案公布的“献血待遇”在制订细则的过程中会作为参考。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;\">用血费用报销一趟不用跑</strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">条例规定，符合免交临床用血费用条件的，可以在就诊医疗机构核销临床用血费用；就诊医疗机构不具备核销条件的，可以携带相关用血凭证到中心血站报销临床用血费用。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">为了方便献血者，从2018年5月起，献血者可通过快递报销材料的方式，办理无偿献血用血费用报销，实现了“用血费用报销一趟不用跑”。合肥市中心血站提醒，报销时所需邮寄材料包括：无偿献血本人报销，需出示出院记录、出院发票、住院用药明细单、身份证、献血证；无偿献血者的直系亲属和配偶报销，除以上证件及材料外，还必须出示用血者身份证，能证明用血者与献血者关系的证件，比如户口簿、结婚证或派出所户籍证明；报销人姓名及联系电话；报销人开户银行及账号。相关报销材料需原件，或加盖公章的复印件。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">无偿献血不仅仅是献血者本人受益，其直系亲属也可以跟着“沾光”。去年，有611名献血者在合肥市中心血站办理了偿还手续，包括献血者本人及献血者的父母、配偶、子女，总计偿还金额67.04万元。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">李婧美 新安晚报 安徽网 大皖客户端记者 叶晓</p>',0,NULL,0,0,2,6,0);
INSERT INTO `t_news` VALUES (253,'池州市长雍成瀚就任省外办党组书记 提名为主任人选','2019-10-30 08:24:26','<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">安徽网 大皖客户端讯 &nbsp;安徽省外办官方网站消息，2019年10月28日下午，省外办召开全体干部大会，宣布省委关于省外办主要领导职务任命的决定。省委组织部常务副部长何军宣读省委决定，雍成瀚同志任省人民政府外事办公室（省人民政府港澳事务办公室）党组书记，提名为省人民政府外事办公室（省人民政府港澳事务办公室）主任人选。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">雍成瀚此前任安徽省池州市委副书记、市长。安徽先锋网于10月27日发布的干部任前公示公告显示：现任安徽省委宣传部副部长操龙灿，拟任池州市委副书记并提名为池州市人民政府市长候选人。<span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">雍成瀚简历(来源：池州市政府网)：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">雍成瀚，男，1964年12月出生，汉族，安徽含山人，大学本科，哲学硕士，公共管理硕士，1985年5月加入中国共产党，1985年7月参加工作。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">1981.09-1985.07 安徽大学中文系学生</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">1985.07-1992.12 安徽大学党委办公室秘书</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">1992.12-1996.04 安徽大学高等教育自学考试办公室主任</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">1996.04-2003.01 安徽大学校长办公室副主任、安徽大学办公室副主任</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">(其间：1997.09-1999.09 安徽大学马克思主义哲学研究生课程进修班学习，2003.06获哲学硕士学位)</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">2003.01-2003.10 省旅游集团有限公司办公室主任</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">2003.10-2007.11 合肥市政府副市长</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">2007.11-2013.06 合肥市委常委、纪委书记</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">(其间：2006.04-2008.01清华大学公共管理学院攻读公共管理硕士学位)</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">2013.06-2013.10 芜湖市委副书记</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">2013.10-2014.05 芜湖市委副书记、市委党校校长</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">2014.05-2014.09 芜湖市委副书记、市委党校校长、芜湖市经济技术开发区党工委第一书记</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">2014.09-2015.08 芜湖市委副书记、市委党校校长、芜湖市经济技术开发区党工委第一书记、市委统战部部长</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">2015.08-2016.01 池州市委副书记、池州市人民政府党组书记、代市长</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">2016.01- 池州市委副书记、池州市人民政府党组书记、市长</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 2.2; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">新安晚报 安徽网 大皖客户端记者 朱春友</p>',0,NULL,0,0,10,6,0),(254,'安徽省政协党组书记、主席张昌尔去合肥工业大学走访调研','2019-10-30 11:51:02','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 8px 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">在中华人民共和国成立70周年之际，10月22日上午，安徽省政协党组书记、主席张昌尔率队来校走访看望省政协委员，并开展调研。校长、党委副书记梁樑陪同调研。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 8px 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">张昌尔首先询问了我校省政协委员的履职情况，并向他们致以亲切问候。张昌尔希望，合工大省政协委员要始终坚持中国共产党的领导，做理论学习的带头人、教书育人的带头人、凝聚共识的带头人，积极履职尽责，发挥政治协商、民主监督、参政议政的作用，为建设现代化五大发展美好安徽贡献力量。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 8px 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">随后，张昌尔走进我校管理学院实验室，听取中国工程院院士杨善林教授及其科研团队成员关于人机协同智能微创医疗装备系统关键技术等领域取得系列成果的汇报，并饶有兴致地体验了内腔镜微创手术仿真训练系统。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 8px 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">在仪器科学与光电工程学院实验室，张昌尔驻足科技成果前仔细观看，详细询问研发和转化等情况，充分肯定了学校所取得的成绩，并对实验室未来发展表达了殷切的希望。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 8px 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">梁樑对张昌尔一行来校访问调研表示热烈欢迎，对省政协长期以来给予学校改革建设发展的关心、指导和帮助表示感谢。他表示，学校将继续秉承“工业报国”之志，抓住“长三角一体化发展”重大发展机遇和有利发展环境，着力为区域经济社会发展作出新的更大贡献。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 8px 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">省政协办公厅、研究室综合处，学校校务部、党政办公室、党委统战部等相关同志参加了走访调研。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 8px 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img title=\"20191023173309773295.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: medium; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: medium; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: medium; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: medium; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; height: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\" src=\"http://news.hfut.edu.cn/uploadfile/image/20191023/20191023173309773295.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 8px 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img title=\"20191023173309641875.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: medium; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: medium; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: medium; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: medium; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; height: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\" src=\"http://news.hfut.edu.cn/uploadfile/image/20191023/20191023173309641875.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 23px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 8px 0px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img title=\"20191023173309698329.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom-color: currentColor; border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: medium; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: currentColor; border-left-style: none; border-left-width: medium; border-right-color: currentColor; border-right-style: none; border-right-width: medium; border-top-color: currentColor; border-top-style: none; border-top-width: medium; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; height: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\" src=\"http://news.hfut.edu.cn/uploadfile/image/20191023/20191023173309698329.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Tahoma, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><div class=\"bk10\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 1px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; height: 10px; line-height: 1px; white-space: normal;\"></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Tahoma, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">\r\n\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: right; white-space: normal;\">（朱玟雅/文&nbsp;&nbsp;宁浪沙/图）&nbsp;&nbsp;<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/>\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Tahoma, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><div class=\"bk10\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 1px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; height: 10px; line-height: 1px; white-space: normal;\"></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Tahoma, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><div class=\"content_editors\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: right; white-space: normal;\">编辑：朱峰</div><p><br/></p>',1,'http://localhost:8080/news/File/20191023173309773295.jpg',1,0,4,6,0),(255,'蚌埠市出台措施全力“增产保供”生猪产业','2019-10-30 11:52:59','<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 14px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">据蚌埠新闻网消息 &nbsp;稳定生猪生产，保障猪肉供应，事关“三农”发展、群众生活和物价稳定。今年以来，围绕稳定恢复生猪生产，着力保障市场供应，全市出台了一揽子扶持政策，打出“增产保供”的“组合拳”。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(108, 108, 108); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, 宋体; font-size: 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 14px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">“生猪生产发展长期受到贷款难、用地难和粪污治理难多种因素的制约。”市农业农村局畜牧兽医水产局副局长苏锡胜表示，落实扶持政策，我市抓住生猪产业转型发展的关键环节，努力保障老百姓的“菜篮子”和养殖场户的“钱袋子”。对存栏能繁母猪50头以上的规模养殖场，每头能繁母猪一次性补贴200元；对生猪规模养殖场从有资质的种猪场（父母代以上）引进母猪的，每引进1头一次性补贴200元，保护种猪生产。对年出栏500头以上规模猪场，购买育肥猪政策性保险的，按照个人承担每头保费的50%补贴；对生猪养殖场户购买商业性保险的育肥猪，按照10元/头给予保费补贴；对采取全进全出育肥猪养殖的规模场，一次性补栏仔猪500头以上的，每头仔猪补贴50元。对年出栏500头以上生猪养殖场的贷款实现贴息，按照实际发生贷款利息的50%补贴；对已获省贴息的种猪场、年出栏5000头以上的规模猪场，剩余利息按照实际发生的50%补贴。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(108, 108, 108); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, 宋体; font-size: 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 14px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">在出台针对性措施，提振生猪养殖信心，稳定生猪生产的同时，市农业部门加大替代品供应，加快发展投入成本低、生长周期短、饲料转化率高的肉鸡、肉鸭和蛋鸡生产，重点推动家禽养殖大户转型升级，推行肉牛、肉羊快速育肥，积极扩大水产养殖规模，稳定肉类市场供应。截至9月底，家禽出栏率同比增长11.16%，肉羊出栏率同比增长11.73%，水产品总产量同比增长2.86%，有效缓解猪肉供应紧张局面。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(108, 108, 108); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, 宋体; font-size: 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 14px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">为贯彻落实全国、全省稳定生猪生产保障市场供应电视电话会议工作部署，按照《关于落实稳定生猪生产保障市场供应若干政策措施的通知》，市政府办公室近日发布关于做好稳定生猪生产保障市场供应的通知，从财政、金融、降成本及疫病防控等方面出台十条措施，覆盖生猪养殖、疫病防控、市场流通等环节，全力“增产保供”生猪产业。（记者 杨露露）</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,1,3,6,0),(256,'池州市1人入选9月份安徽好人榜','2019-10-30 11:53:39','<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 14px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">安徽网 大皖客户端讯 据池州市人民政府发布，日前，9月份“安徽好人”榜单揭晓，池州市田玉榜上有名。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(108, 108, 108); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, 宋体; font-size: 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 14px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal;\">今年55岁的田玉是东至县种植业管理局职工，同时也是池州市“三献”协会会员、东至县义工协会会员、东至县冬泳协会会员。2001年以来，田玉累计无偿献血13000毫升，先后荣获2012—2013年度全国无偿献血奉献奖铜奖、2014—2015年度全国无偿奉献奖银奖、2016年池州市“三献”志愿者协会“五星级志愿者”以及2017安徽省年度“十大献血之星”提名奖等荣誉。作为东至冬泳协会的一名老游泳队员，田玉义务指导不同年龄段的爱好者学习游泳，义务留守游泳基地值班，防止青少年溺水事件发生，成功救起过10余名溺水者。</p><p><br/></p>',0,NULL,0,0,1,6,0);

